33//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
34const char* Avc_profile_idc(int8u profile_idc)
35{
36 switch (profile_idc)
37 {
38 case 44 : return "CAVLC 4:4:4 Intra";
39 case 66 : return "Baseline";
40 case 77 : return "Main";
41 case 83 : return "Scalable Baseline";
42 case 86 : return "Scalable High";
43 case 88 : return "Extended";
44 case 100 : return "High";
45 case 110 : return "High 10";
46 case 118 : return "Multiview High";
47 case 122 : return "High 4:2:2";
48 case 128 : return "Stereo High";
49 case 138 : return "Multiview Depth High";
50 case 144 : return "High 4:4:4";
51 case 244 : return "High 4:4:4 Predictive";
52 default : return "";
53 }
54}

263//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
264const char* Avc_user_data_GA94_cc_type(int8u cc_type)
265{
266 switch (cc_type)
267 {
268 case 0 : return "CEA-608 line 21 field 1 closed captions"; //closed caption 3 if this is second field
269 case 1 : return "CEA-608 line 21 field 2 closed captions"; //closed caption 4 if this is second field
270 case 2 : return "DTVCC Channel Packet Data";
271 case 3 : return "DTVCC Channel Packet Start";
272 default : return "";
273 }
274}
275
276//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
277int32u Avc_MaxDpbMbs(int8u level)
278{
279 switch (level)
280 {
281 case 10 : return 1485;
282 case 11 : return 3000;
283 case 12 : return 6000;
284 case 13 :
285 case 20 : return 11880;
286 case 21 : return 19800;
287 case 22 : return 20250;
288 case 30 : return 40500;
289 case 31 : return 108000;
290 case 32 : return 216000;
291 case 40 :
292 case 41 : return 245760;
293 case 42 : return 522240;
294 case 50 : return 589824;
295 case 51 : return 983040;
296 default : return 0;
297 }
298}

378//***************************************************************************
379// Constructor/Destructor

381
382//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
383File_Avc::File_Avc()
384#if MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
385:File__Duplicate()
386#endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
387{
388 //Config
389 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
390 ParserIDs[0]=MediaInfo_Parser_Avc;
391 StreamIDs_Width[0]=0;
392 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
393 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
394 Trace_Layers_Update(8); //Stream
395 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
396 MustSynchronize=true;
397 Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched_Max=64*1024;
398 PTS_DTS_Needed=true;
399 IsRawStream=true;
400 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded=0;
401
402 //In
403 Frame_Count_Valid=MediaInfoLib::Config.ParseSpeed_Get()>=0.3?512:2;
404 FrameIsAlwaysComplete=false;
405 MustParse_SPS_PPS=false;
406 SizedBlocks=false;
407
408 //Temporal references
409 TemporalReferences_DelayedElement=NULL;
410
411 //Text
412 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
413 GA94_03_Parser=NULL;
414 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
415}
416
417//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
418File_Avc::~File_Avc()
419{
420 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReferences.size(); Pos++)
421 delete TemporalReferences[Pos]; //TemporalReferences[Pos]=NULL;
422 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
423 delete GA94_03_Parser; //GA94_03_Parser=NULL;
424 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
425
426 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<seq_parameter_sets.size(); Pos++)
427 delete seq_parameter_sets[Pos]; //TemporalReferences[Pos]=NULL;
428
429 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<subset_seq_parameter_sets.size(); Pos++)
430 delete subset_seq_parameter_sets[Pos]; //TemporalReferences[Pos]=NULL;
431
432 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<pic_parameter_sets.size(); Pos++)
433 delete pic_parameter_sets[Pos]; //TemporalReferences[Pos]=NULL;
434}

436//***************************************************************************
437// AVC-Intra hardcoded headers
438//***************************************************************************
439
440//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
441File_Avc::avcintra_header File_Avc::AVC_Intra_Headers_Data(int32u CodecID)
442{
443 switch (CodecID)
444 {
445 case 0x61693132: //ai12
446 case 0x61693232: //ai22
447 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080p50_100, AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080p50_100_Size); // AVC-Intra 1080p50 class 100/200
448 case 0x61693133: //ai13
449 case 0x61693233: //ai23
450 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080p60_100, AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080p60_100_Size); // AVC-Intra 1080p60 class 100/200
451 case 0x61693135: //ai15
452 case 0x61693235: //ai25
453 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i50_100, AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i50_100_Size); // AVC-Intra 1080i50 class 100/200
454 case 0x61693136: //ai16
455 case 0x61693236: //ai26
456 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i60_100, AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i60_100_Size); // AVC-Intra 1080i60 class 100/200
457 case 0x61693170: //ai1p
458 case 0x61693270: //ai2p
459 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p60_100, AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p60_100_Size); // AVC-Intra 720p60 class 100/200
460 case 0x61693171: //ai1q
461 case 0x61693271: //ai2q
462 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p50_100, AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p50_100_Size); // AVC-Intra 720p50 class 100/200
463 //case 0x61693532: //ai52
464 // return avcintra_header(NULL, 0); // AVC-Intra 1080p25 class 50 (not supported)
465 //case 0x61693533: //ai53
466 // return avcintra_header(NULL, 0); // AVC-Intra 1080p30 class 50 (not supported)
467 case 0x61693535: //ai55
468 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i50__50, AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i50__50_Size); // AVC-Intra 1080i50 class 50
469 case 0x61693536: //ai56
470 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i60__50, AVC_Intra_Headers::_1080i60__50_Size); // AVC-Intra 1080i60 class 50
471 case 0x61693570: //ai5p
472 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p60__50, AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p60__50_Size); // AVC-Intra 720p60 class 50
473 case 0x61693571: //ai5q
474 return avcintra_header(AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p50__50, AVC_Intra_Headers::__720p50__50_Size); // AVC-Intra 720p50 class 50
475 default :
476 return avcintra_header(NULL, 0);
477 }
478}
479
480//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
481int32u File_Avc::AVC_Intra_CodecID_FromMeta(int32u Height, int32u Fields, int32u SampleDuration, int32u TimeScale, int32u SizePerFrame)
482{
483 // Computing bitrate
484 int64u BitRate=((int64u)SizePerFrame)*8*TimeScale/SampleDuration;
485 int64u SampleRate=float64_int64s(((float64)TimeScale)/SampleDuration);
486 int32u Class=BitRate<=75000000?50:100; //Arbitrary choosen. TODO: check real maximumm bitrate, check class 200
487 switch (Class)
488 {
489 case 100 :
490 switch (Height)
491 {
492 case 1080 :
493 switch (Fields)
494 {
495 case 1:
496 switch (SampleRate)
497 {
498 case 50: return 0x61693132; //ai12
499 case 60: return 0x61693133; //ai13
500 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
501 }
502 case 2:
503 switch (SampleRate)
504 {
505 case 25: return 0x61693135; //ai15 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
506 case 30: return 0x61693136; //ai16 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
507 case 50: return 0x61693135; //ai15 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
508 case 60: return 0x61693136; //ai16 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
509 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
510 }
511 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
512 }
513 case 720 :
514 switch (Fields)
515 {
516 case 1:
517 switch (SampleRate)
518 {
519 case 50: return 0x61693170; //ai1p
520 case 60: return 0x61693171; //ai1q
521 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
522 }
523 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
524 }
525 default : return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
526 }
527 case 50 :
528 switch (Height)
529 {
530 case 1080 :
531 switch (Fields)
532 {
533 case 1:
534 switch (SampleRate)
535 {
536 case 25: return 0x61693532; //ai52
537 case 30: return 0x61693533; //ai53
538 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
539 }
540 case 2:
541 switch (SampleRate)
542 {
543 case 25: return 0x61693535; //ai55 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
544 case 30: return 0x61693536; //ai56 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
545 case 50: return 0x61693535; //ai55 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
546 case 60: return 0x61693536; //ai56 //TODO: check more files in order to know if it should be 1 or 2 fields per sample
547 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
548 }
549 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
550 }
551 case 720 :
552 switch (Fields)
553 {
554 case 1:
555 switch (SampleRate)
556 {
557 case 50: return 0x61693570; //ai5p
558 case 60: return 0x61693571; //ai5q
559 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
560 }
561 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
562 }
563 default : return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
564 }
565 default: return 0x4156696E; //AVin (neutral)
566 }
567}

573//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
574void File_Avc::Streams_Fill()
575{
576 for (std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin(); seq_parameter_set_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++seq_parameter_set_Item)
577 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item))
578 Streams_Fill(seq_parameter_set_Item);
579 for (std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator subset_seq_parameter_set_Item=subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin(); subset_seq_parameter_set_Item!=subset_seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++subset_seq_parameter_set_Item)
580 if ((*subset_seq_parameter_set_Item))
581 {
582 if (seq_parameter_sets.empty())
583 Streams_Fill(subset_seq_parameter_set_Item);
584 else
585 Streams_Fill_subset(subset_seq_parameter_set_Item);
586 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_MultiView_Count, (*subset_seq_parameter_set_Item)->num_views_minus1+1);
587 }
588
589 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
590 for (size_t Pos = 0; Pos<Dump_SPS.size(); Pos++)
591 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "Dump_seq_parameter_set", Dump_SPS[Pos].c_str());
592 for (size_t Pos = 0; Pos<Dump_PPS.size(); Pos++)
593 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, "Dump_pic_parameter_set", Dump_PPS[Pos].c_str());
594 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
595}
596
597//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
598void File_Avc::Streams_Fill(std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item)
599{
600 //Calculating - Pixels
601 int32u Width =((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_width_in_mbs_minus1 +1)*16;
602 int32u Height=((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_height_in_map_units_minus1+1)*16*(2-(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag);
603 int32u CropUnitX=Avc_SubWidthC [(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->ChromaArrayType()];
604 int32u CropUnitY=Avc_SubHeightC[(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->ChromaArrayType()]*(2-(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag);
605 Width -=((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_left_offset+(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_right_offset )*CropUnitX;
606 Height-=((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_top_offset +(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_bottom_offset)*CropUnitY;
607
608 //From vui_parameters
609 float64 PixelAspectRatio=1;
610 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters)
611 {
612 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_info_present_flag)
613 {
614 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_idc<Avc_PixelAspectRatio_Size)
615 PixelAspectRatio=Avc_PixelAspectRatio[(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_idc];
616 else if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_idc==0xFF && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->sar_height)
617 PixelAspectRatio=((float64)(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->sar_width)/(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->sar_height;
618 }
619 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->timing_info_present_flag)
620 {
621 if (!(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->fixed_frame_rate_flag)
622 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_FrameRate_Mode, "VFR");
623 else if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->timing_info_present_flag && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->time_scale && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->num_units_in_tick)
624 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_FrameRate, (float64)(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->time_scale/(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->num_units_in_tick/((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag?2:((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==2?1:2))/FrameRate_Divider);
625 }
626
627 //Colour description
628 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->video_signal_type_present_flag)
629 {
630 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Standard, Avc_video_format[(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->video_format]);
631 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_colour_range, Avc_video_full_range[(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->video_full_range_flag]);
632 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->colour_description_present_flag)
633 {
634 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_colour_description_present, "Yes");
635 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_colour_primaries, Mpegv_colour_primaries((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->colour_primaries));
636 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_transfer_characteristics, Mpegv_transfer_characteristics((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->transfer_characteristics));
637 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_matrix_coefficients, Mpegv_matrix_coefficients((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->matrix_coefficients));
638 }
639 }
640
641 //hrd_parameter_sets
642 int64u bit_rate_value=(int64u)-1;
643 bool bit_rate_value_IsValid=true;
644 bool cbr_flag=false;
645 bool cbr_flag_IsSet=false;
646 bool cbr_flag_IsValid=true;
647 seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct::xxl* NAL=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL;
648 if (NAL)
649 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<NAL->SchedSel.size(); Pos++)
650 {
651 if (NAL->SchedSel[Pos].cpb_size_value!=(int32u)-1)
652 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BufferSize, NAL->SchedSel[Pos].cpb_size_value);
653 if (bit_rate_value!=(int64u)-1 && bit_rate_value!=NAL->SchedSel[Pos].bit_rate_value)
654 bit_rate_value_IsValid=false;
655 if (bit_rate_value==(int64u)-1)
656 bit_rate_value=NAL->SchedSel[Pos].bit_rate_value;
657 if (cbr_flag_IsSet==true && cbr_flag!=NAL->SchedSel[Pos].cbr_flag)
658 cbr_flag_IsValid=false;
659 if (cbr_flag_IsSet==0)
660 {
661 cbr_flag=NAL->SchedSel[Pos].cbr_flag;
662 cbr_flag_IsSet=true;
663 }
664 }
665 seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct::xxl* VCL=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->VCL;
666 if (VCL)
667 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<VCL->SchedSel.size(); Pos++)
668 {
669 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BufferSize, VCL->SchedSel[Pos].cpb_size_value);
670 if (bit_rate_value!=(int64u)-1 && bit_rate_value!=VCL->SchedSel[Pos].bit_rate_value)
671 bit_rate_value_IsValid=false;
672 if (bit_rate_value==(int64u)-1)
673 bit_rate_value=VCL->SchedSel[Pos].bit_rate_value;
674 if (cbr_flag_IsSet==true && cbr_flag!=VCL->SchedSel[Pos].cbr_flag)
675 cbr_flag_IsValid=false;
676 if (cbr_flag_IsSet==0)
677 {
678 cbr_flag=VCL->SchedSel[Pos].cbr_flag;
679 cbr_flag_IsSet=true;
680 }
681 }
682 if (cbr_flag_IsSet && cbr_flag_IsValid)
683 {
684 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate_Mode, cbr_flag?"CBR":"VBR");
685 if (bit_rate_value!=(int64u)-1 && bit_rate_value_IsValid)
686 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, cbr_flag?Video_BitRate_Nominal:Video_BitRate_Maximum, bit_rate_value);
687 }
688 }
689
690 if (Count_Get(Stream_Video)==0)
691 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Video);
692 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format, "AVC");
693 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec, "AVC");
694
695 Ztring Profile=Ztring().From_Local(Avc_profile_idc((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->profile_idc));
696 switch ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->profile_idc)
697 {
698 case 44 : // CAVLC 4:4:4 Intra
699 case 100 : // High
700 case 110 : // High 10
701 case 122 : // High 4:2:2"
702 case 244 : // High 4:4:4 Predictive
703 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->constraint_set3_flag)
704 Profile+=__T(" Intra");
705 }
706 Profile+=__T("@L")+Ztring().From_Number(((float)(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->level_idc)/10, ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->level_idc%10)?1:0);
707 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile, Profile);
708 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Profile, Profile);
709 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Width, Width);
710 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Height, Height);
711 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_left_offset || (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_right_offset)
712 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Stored_Width, ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_width_in_mbs_minus1 +1)*16);
713 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_top_offset || (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_crop_bottom_offset)
714 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Stored_Height, ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_height_in_map_units_minus1+1)*16*(2-(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag));
715 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_PixelAspectRatio, PixelAspectRatio, 3, true);
716 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_DisplayAspectRatio, Width*PixelAspectRatio/Height, 3, true); //More precise
717 if (FrameRate_Divider==2)
718 {
719 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Settings_FrameMode, "Frame doubling");
720 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Settings, "Frame doubling");
721 }
722 if (FrameRate_Divider==3)
723 {
724 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Settings_FrameMode, "Frame tripling");
725 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos_Last, Video_Format_Settings, "Frame tripling");
726 }
727
728 //Interlacement
729 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->mb_adaptive_frame_field_flag && Structure_Frame>0) //Interlaced macro-block
730 {
731 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "MBAFF");
732 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "MBAFF");
733 }
734 else if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag || (Structure_Frame>0 && Structure_Field==0)) //No interlaced frame
735 {
736 switch ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_struct_FirstDetected)
737 {
738 case 3 :
739 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Interlaced");
740 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "TFF");
741 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_PictureStructure, "Frame");
742 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "InterleavedFields");
743 break;
744 case 4 :
745 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Interlaced");
746 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "BFF");
747 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_PictureStructure, "Frame");
748 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "InterleavedFields");
749 break;
750 default :
751 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Progressive");
752 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "PPF");
753 }
754 }
755 else if (Structure_Field>0)
756 {
757 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType, "Interlaced");
758 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, "Interlaced");
759 }
760 std::string ScanOrders, PictureTypes(PictureTypes_PreviousFrames);
761 ScanOrders.reserve(TemporalReferences.size());
762 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReferences.size(); Pos++)
763 if (TemporalReferences[Pos])
764 {
765 ScanOrders+=TemporalReferences[Pos]->IsTop?'T':'B';
766 if ((Pos%2)==0)
767 PictureTypes+=Avc_slice_type[TemporalReferences[Pos]->slice_type];
768 }
769 else if (!PictureTypes.empty()) //Only if stream already started
770 {
771 ScanOrders+=' ';
772 if ((Pos%2)==0)
773 PictureTypes+=' ';
774 }
775 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, ScanOrder_Detect(ScanOrders));
776 { //Legacy
777 string Result=ScanOrder_Detect(ScanOrders);
778 if (!Result.empty())
779 {
780 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Interlacement, Result, true, true);
781 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "SeparatedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
782 }
783 else
784 {
785 switch ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_struct_FirstDetected)
786 {
787 case 1 :
788 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, (string) "TFF");
789 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "SeparatedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
790 break;
791 case 2 :
792 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, (string) "BFF");
793 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "SeparatedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
794 break;
795 case 3 :
796 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, (string) "TFF");
797 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "InterleavedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
798 break;
799 case 4 :
800 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanOrder, (string) "BFF");
801 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ScanType_StoreMethod, "InterleavedFields", Unlimited, true, true);
802 break;
803 default : ;
804 }
805 }
806 }
807 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_GOP, GOP_Detect(PictureTypes));
808
809 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library, Encoded_Library);
810 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library_Name, Encoded_Library_Name);
811 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library_Version, Encoded_Library_Version);
812 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Encoded_Library_Settings, Encoded_Library_Settings);
813 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library, Encoded_Library);
814 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library_Name, Encoded_Library_Name);
815 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library_Version, Encoded_Library_Version);
816 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Encoded_Library_Settings, Encoded_Library_Settings);
817 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitRate_Nominal, BitRate_Nominal);
818 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_MuxingMode, MuxingMode);
819 for (std::vector<pic_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator pic_parameter_set_Item=pic_parameter_sets.begin(); pic_parameter_set_Item!=pic_parameter_sets.end(); ++pic_parameter_set_Item)
820 if (*pic_parameter_set_Item && (*pic_parameter_set_Item)->seq_parameter_set_id==seq_parameter_set_Item-(seq_parameter_sets.empty()?subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin():seq_parameter_sets.begin()))
821 {
822 if ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->entropy_coding_mode_flag)
823 {
824 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings, "CABAC");
825 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_CABAC, "Yes");
826 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings, "CABAC");
827 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings_CABAC, "Yes");
828 }
829 else
830 {
831 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_CABAC, "No");
832 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings_CABAC, "No");
833 }
834 break; //TODO: currently, testing only the first pic_parameter_set
835 }
836 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames>0)
837 {
838 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings, Ztring::ToZtring((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames)+__T(" Ref Frames"));
839 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings, Ztring::ToZtring((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames)+__T(" Ref Frames"));
840 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Settings_RefFrames, (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames);
841 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Codec_Settings_RefFrames, (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames);
842 }
843 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->matrix_coefficients == 0)
844 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ColorSpace, "RGB");
845 else
846 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_ColorSpace, "YUV");
847 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Colorimetry, Avc_Colorimetry_format_idc[(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->chroma_format_idc]);
848 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->bit_depth_luma_minus8==(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->bit_depth_chroma_minus8)
849 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_BitDepth, (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->bit_depth_luma_minus8+8);
850}
851
852//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
853void File_Avc::Streams_Fill_subset(const std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item)
854{
855 Ztring Profile=Ztring().From_Local(Avc_profile_idc((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->profile_idc))+__T("@L")+Ztring().From_Number(((float)(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->level_idc)/10, 1);
856 Ztring Profile_Base=Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile);
857 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile, Profile, true);
858 if (!Profile_Base.empty())
859 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile, Profile_Base);
860}
861
862//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
863void File_Avc::Streams_Finish()
864{
865 if (PTS_End!=(int64u)-1 && (IsSub || File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Size==File_Size))
866 {
867 if (PTS_End>PTS_Begin)
868 Fill(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Duration, float64_int64s(((float64)(PTS_End-PTS_Begin))/1000000));
869 }
870
871 //GA94 captions
872 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
873 if (GA94_03_Parser && GA94_03_Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
874 {
875 Clear(Stream_Text);
876
877 Finish(GA94_03_Parser);
878 Merge(*GA94_03_Parser);
879
880 Ztring LawRating=GA94_03_Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating);
881 if (!LawRating.empty())
882 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating, LawRating, true);
883 Ztring Title=GA94_03_Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title);
884 if (!Title.empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty())
885 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Title, Title);
886
887 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Text); Pos++)
888 {
889 Ztring MuxingMode=Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, "MuxingMode");
890 Fill(Stream_Text, Pos, "MuxingMode", __T("SCTE 128 / ")+MuxingMode, true);
891 }
892 }
893 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
894
895 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
896 if (seq_parameter_sets.size()==1 && (*seq_parameter_sets.begin())->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_sets.begin())->vui_parameters->timing_info_present_flag && (*seq_parameter_sets.begin())->vui_parameters->fixed_frame_rate_flag)
897 Ibi_Stream_Finish((*seq_parameter_sets.begin())->vui_parameters->time_scale, (*seq_parameter_sets.begin())->vui_parameters->num_units_in_tick);
898 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
899}

901//***************************************************************************
902// Buffer - File header
903//***************************************************************************
904
905//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
906bool File_Avc::FileHeader_Begin()
907{
908 if (!File__Analyze::FileHeader_Begin_0x000001())
909 return false;
910
911 if (!MustSynchronize)
912 {
913 Synched_Init();
914 Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched=0;
915 File_Offset_FirstSynched=File_Offset;
916 }
917
918 //All should be OK
919 return true;
920}
921
922//***************************************************************************
923// Buffer - Synchro
924//***************************************************************************
925
926//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
927bool File_Avc::Synchronize()
928{
929 //Synchronizing
930 size_t Buffer_Offset_Min=Buffer_Offset;
931 while(Buffer_Offset+4<=Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
932 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
933 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x01))
934 {
935 Buffer_Offset+=2;
936 while(Buffer_Offset<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset]!=0x00)
937 Buffer_Offset+=2;
938 if (Buffer_Offset>=Buffer_Size || Buffer[Buffer_Offset-1]==0x00)
939 Buffer_Offset--;
940 }
941 if (Buffer_Offset>Buffer_Offset_Min && Buffer[Buffer_Offset-1]==0x00)
942 Buffer_Offset--;
943
944 //Parsing last bytes if needed
945 if (Buffer_Offset+4==Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
946 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
947 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x00
948 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]!=0x01))
949 Buffer_Offset++;
950 if (Buffer_Offset+3==Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
951 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
952 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x01))
953 Buffer_Offset++;
954 if (Buffer_Offset+2==Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
955 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00))
956 Buffer_Offset++;
957 if (Buffer_Offset+1==Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00)
958 Buffer_Offset++;
959
960 if (Buffer_Offset+4>Buffer_Size)
961 return false;
962
963 //Synched is OK
964 Synched=true;
965 return true;
966}
967
968//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
969bool File_Avc::Synched_Test()
970{
971 //Must have enough buffer for having header
972 if (Buffer_Offset+6>Buffer_Size)
973 return false;
974
975 //Quick test of synchro
976 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]!=0x00
977 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]!=0x00
978 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x01 && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]!=0x00 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]!=0x01)))
979 {
980 Synched=false;
981 return true;
982 }
983
984 //Quick search
985 if (!Header_Parser_QuickSearch())
986 return false;
987
988 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
989 bool zero_byte=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x00;
990 bool RandomAccess=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1F)==0x07 || ((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1F)==0x09 && ((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?5:4)]&0xE0)==0x00 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?5:4)]&0xE0)==0xA0)); //seq_parameter_set or access_unit_delimiter with value=0 or 5 (3 bits)
991 if (RandomAccess)
992 Ibi_Add();
993 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
994
995 //We continue
996 return true;
997}

999//***************************************************************************
1000// Buffer - Demux
1001//***************************************************************************
1002
1003//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1004#if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1005bool File_Avc::Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Test()
1006{
1007 const int8u* Buffer_Temp=NULL;
1008 size_t Buffer_Temp_Size=0;
1009 bool RandomAccess=true; //Default, in case of problem
1010
1011 if ((MustParse_SPS_PPS || SizedBlocks) && Demux_Avc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_Iso14496_10)
1012 {
1013 if (MustParse_SPS_PPS)
1014 return true; //Wait for SPS and PPS
1015
1016 //Random access check
1017 RandomAccess=false;
1018
1019 //Computing final size
1020 size_t TranscodedBuffer_Size=0;
1021 while (Buffer_Offset+SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1+1<=Buffer_Size)
1022 {
1023 size_t Size;
1024 switch (SizeOfNALU_Minus1)
1025 {
1026 case 0: Size=Buffer[Buffer_Offset];
1027 TranscodedBuffer_Size+=2;
1028 break;
1029 case 1: Size=BigEndian2int16u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset);
1030 TranscodedBuffer_Size++;
1031 break;
1032 case 2: Size=BigEndian2int24u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset);
1033 break;
1034 case 3: Size=BigEndian2int32u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset);
1035 TranscodedBuffer_Size--;
1036 break;
1037 default: return true; //Problem
1038 }
1039 Size+=SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1;
1040
1041 //Coherency checking
1042 if (Size==0 || Buffer_Offset+Size>Buffer_Size || (Buffer_Offset+Size!=Buffer_Size && Buffer_Offset+Size+SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1>Buffer_Size))
1043 Size=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset;
1044
1045 //Random access check
1046 if (!RandomAccess && Buffer_Offset+SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1<Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1]&0x1F) && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1]&0x1F)<=5) //Is a slice
1047 {
1048 int32u slice_type;
1049 Element_Offset=SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1+1;
1050 Element_Size=Size;
1051 BS_Begin();
1052 Skip_UE("first_mb_in_slice");
1053 Get_UE (slice_type, "slice_type");
1054 BS_End();
1055 Element_Offset=0;
1056
1057 switch (slice_type)
1058 {
1059 case 2 :
1060 case 7 :
1061 RandomAccess=true;
1062 }
1063 }
1064
1065 TranscodedBuffer_Size+=Size;
1066 Buffer_Offset+=Size;
1067 }
1068 Buffer_Offset=0;
1069
1070 //Adding SPS/PPS sizes
1071 if (RandomAccess)
1072 {
1073 for (seq_parameter_set_structs::iterator Data_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin(); Data_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++Data_Item)
1074 TranscodedBuffer_Size+=(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size;
1075 for (seq_parameter_set_structs::iterator Data_Item=subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin(); Data_Item!=subset_seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++Data_Item)
1076 TranscodedBuffer_Size+=(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size;
1077 for (pic_parameter_set_structs::iterator Data_Item=pic_parameter_sets.begin(); Data_Item!=pic_parameter_sets.end(); ++Data_Item)
1078 TranscodedBuffer_Size+=(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size;
1079 }
1080
1081 //Copying
1082 int8u* TranscodedBuffer=new int8u[TranscodedBuffer_Size+100];
1083 size_t TranscodedBuffer_Pos=0;
1084 if (RandomAccess)
1085 {
1086 for (seq_parameter_set_structs::iterator Data_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin(); Data_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++Data_Item)
1087 {
1088 std::memcpy(TranscodedBuffer+TranscodedBuffer_Pos, (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer, (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size);
1089 TranscodedBuffer_Pos+=(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size;
1090 }
1091 for (seq_parameter_set_structs::iterator Data_Item=subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin(); Data_Item!=subset_seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++Data_Item)
1092 {
1093 std::memcpy(TranscodedBuffer+TranscodedBuffer_Pos, (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer, (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size);
1094 TranscodedBuffer_Pos+=(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size;
1095 }
1096 for (pic_parameter_set_structs::iterator Data_Item=pic_parameter_sets.begin(); Data_Item!=pic_parameter_sets.end(); ++Data_Item)
1097 {
1098 std::memcpy(TranscodedBuffer+TranscodedBuffer_Pos, (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer, (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size);
1099 TranscodedBuffer_Pos+=(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size;
1100 }
1101 }
1102 while (Buffer_Offset<Buffer_Size)
1103 {
1104 //Sync layer
1105 TranscodedBuffer[TranscodedBuffer_Pos]=0x00;
1106 TranscodedBuffer_Pos++;
1107 TranscodedBuffer[TranscodedBuffer_Pos]=0x00;
1108 TranscodedBuffer_Pos++;
1109 TranscodedBuffer[TranscodedBuffer_Pos]=0x01;
1110 TranscodedBuffer_Pos++;
1111
1112 //Block
1113 size_t Size;
1114 switch (SizeOfNALU_Minus1)
1115 {
1116 case 0: Size=Buffer[Buffer_Offset];
1117 Buffer_Offset++;
1118 break;
1119 case 1: Size=BigEndian2int16u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset);
1120 Buffer_Offset+=2;
1121 break;
1122 case 2: Size=BigEndian2int24u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset);
1123 Buffer_Offset+=3;
1124 break;
1125 case 3: Size=BigEndian2int32u(Buffer+Buffer_Offset);
1126 Buffer_Offset+=4;
1127 break;
1128 default: //Problem
1129 delete [] TranscodedBuffer;
1130 return false;
1131 }
1132
1133 //Coherency checking
1134 if (Size==0 || Buffer_Offset+Size>Buffer_Size || (Buffer_Offset+Size!=Buffer_Size && Buffer_Offset+Size+SizeOfNALU_Minus1+1>Buffer_Size))
1135 Size=Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset;
1136
1137 std::memcpy(TranscodedBuffer+TranscodedBuffer_Pos, Buffer+Buffer_Offset, Size);
1138 TranscodedBuffer_Pos+=Size;
1139 Buffer_Offset+=Size;
1140 }
1141 Buffer_Offset=0;
1142
1143 Buffer_Temp=Buffer;
1144 Buffer=TranscodedBuffer;
1145 Buffer_Temp_Size=Buffer_Size;
1146 Buffer_Size=TranscodedBuffer_Size;
1147 Demux_Offset=Buffer_Size;
1148 }
1149 else
1150 {
1151 bool zero_byte=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x00;
1152 if (!(((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1B)==0x01 && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?5:4)]&0x80)!=0x80)
1153 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1F)==0x0C))
1154 {
1155 if (Demux_Offset==0)
1156 {
1157 Demux_Offset=Buffer_Offset;
1158 Demux_IntermediateItemFound=false;
1159 }
1160 while (Demux_Offset+6<=Buffer_Size)
1161 {
1162 //Synchronizing
1163 while(Demux_Offset+6<=Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Demux_Offset ]!=0x00
1164 || Buffer[Demux_Offset+1]!=0x00
1165 || Buffer[Demux_Offset+2]!=0x01))
1166 {
1167 Demux_Offset+=2;
1168 while(Demux_Offset<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset]!=0x00)
1169 Demux_Offset+=2;
1170 if (Demux_Offset>=Buffer_Size || Buffer[Demux_Offset-1]==0x00)
1171 Demux_Offset--;
1172 }
1173
1174 if (Demux_Offset+6>Buffer_Size)
1175 {
1176 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Size==File_Size)
1177 Demux_Offset=Buffer_Size;
1178 break;
1179 }
1180
1181 zero_byte=Buffer[Demux_Offset+2]==0x00;
1182 if (Demux_IntermediateItemFound)
1183 {
1184 if (!(((Buffer[Demux_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1B)==0x01 && (Buffer[Demux_Offset+(zero_byte?5:4)]&0x80)!=0x80)
1185 || (Buffer[Demux_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1F)==0x0C))
1186 break;
1187 }
1188 else
1189 {
1190 if ((Buffer[Demux_Offset+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1B)==0x01 && (Buffer[Demux_Offset+(zero_byte?5:4)]&0x80)==0x80)
1191 Demux_IntermediateItemFound=true;
1192 }
1193
1194 Demux_Offset++;
1195 }
1196
1197 if (Demux_Offset+6>Buffer_Size && !FrameIsAlwaysComplete && File_Offset+Buffer_Size<File_Size)
1198 return false; //No complete frame
1199
1200 if (Demux_Offset && Buffer[Demux_Offset-1]==0x00)
1201 Demux_Offset--;
1202
1203 zero_byte=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x00;
1204 size_t Buffer_Offset_Random=Buffer_Offset;
1205 if ((Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Random+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1F)==0x09)
1206 {
1207 Buffer_Offset_Random++;
1208 if (zero_byte)
1209 Buffer_Offset_Random++;
1210 while(Buffer_Offset_Random+6<=Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Random ]!=0x00
1211 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Random+1]!=0x00
1212 || Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Random+2]!=0x01))
1213 Buffer_Offset_Random++;
1214 zero_byte=Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Random+2]==0x00;
1215 }
1216 RandomAccess=Buffer_Offset_Random+6<=Buffer_Size && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Random+(zero_byte?4:3)]&0x1F)==0x07; //seq_parameter_set
1217 }
1218 }
1219
1220 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
1221 {
1222 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1223 return false;
1224 File_Avc* MI=new File_Avc;
1225 Element_Code=(int64u)-1;
1226 Open_Buffer_Init(MI);
1227 Open_Buffer_Continue(MI, Buffer, Buffer_Size);
1228 bool IsOk=MI->Status[IsAccepted];
1229 delete MI;
1230 if (!IsOk)
1231 return false;
1232 }
1233
1234 if (IFrame_Count || RandomAccess)
1235 {
1236 bool Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded_PlusOne=false;
1237 int64u PTS_Temp=FrameInfo.PTS;
1238 if (!IsSub)
1239 FrameInfo.PTS=(int64u)-1;
1240 if (Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1 && Interlaced_Top!=Interlaced_Bottom)
1241 {
1242 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded--;
1243 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded_PlusOne=true;
1244 }
1245 Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Demux(RandomAccess);
1246 if (!IsSub)
1247 FrameInfo.PTS=PTS_Temp;
1248 if (Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded_PlusOne)
1249 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded++;
1250 }
1251 else
1252 Demux_UnpacketizeContainer_Demux_Clear();
1253
1254 if (Buffer_Temp)
1255 {
1256 Demux_TotalBytes-=Buffer_Size;
1257 Demux_TotalBytes+=Buffer_Temp_Size;
1258 delete[] Buffer;
1259 Buffer=Buffer_Temp;
1260 Buffer_Size=Buffer_Temp_Size;
1261 }
1262
1263 return true;
1264}
1265#endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX

1351//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1352void File_Avc::Read_Buffer_Unsynched()
1353{
1354 //Temporal references
1355 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReferences.size(); Pos++)
1356 delete TemporalReferences[Pos]; //TemporalReferences[Pos]=NULL;
1357 TemporalReferences.clear();
1358 delete TemporalReferences_DelayedElement; TemporalReferences_DelayedElement=NULL;
1359 TemporalReferences_Min=0;
1360 TemporalReferences_Max=0;
1361 TemporalReferences_Reserved=0;
1362 TemporalReferences_Offset=0;
1363 TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last=0;
1364 TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min=0;
1365
1366 //Text
1367 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1368 if (GA94_03_Parser)
1369 GA94_03_Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1370 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
1371
1372 //parameter_sets
1373 if (SizedBlocks) //If sized blocks, it is not a broadcasted stream so SPS/PPS are only in container header, we must not disable them.
1374 {
1375 //Rebuilding immediatly TemporalReferences
1376 for (std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin(); seq_parameter_set_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++seq_parameter_set_Item)
1377 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item))
1378 {
1379 size_t MaxNumber;
1380 switch ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type)
1381 {
1382 case 0 : MaxNumber=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxPicOrderCntLsb; break;
1383 case 2 : MaxNumber=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxFrameNum*2; break;
1384 default: Trusted_IsNot("Not supported"); return;
1385 }
1386
1387 TemporalReferences.resize(4*MaxNumber);
1388 TemporalReferences_Reserved=MaxNumber;
1389 }
1390 }
1391 else
1392 {
1393 seq_parameter_sets.clear();
1394 subset_seq_parameter_sets.clear();
1395 pic_parameter_sets.clear();
1396 }
1397
1398 //Status
1399 Interlaced_Top=0;
1400 Interlaced_Bottom=0;
1401 prevPicOrderCntMsb=0;
1402 prevPicOrderCntLsb=(int32u)-1;
1403 prevTopFieldOrderCnt=(int32u)-1;
1404 prevFrameNum=(int32u)-1;
1405 prevFrameNumOffset=(int32u)-1;
1406
1407 //Temp
1408 FrameRate_Divider=1;
1409 FirstPFrameInGop_IsParsed=false;
1410 tc=0;
1411
1412 //Impossible to know TimeStamps now
1413 PTS_End=0;
1414 DTS_End=0;
1415}

1417//***************************************************************************
1418// Buffer - Per element
1419//***************************************************************************
1420
1421//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1422void File_Avc::Header_Parse()
1423{
1424 //Specific case
1425 if (MustParse_SPS_PPS)
1426 {
1427 Header_Fill_Size(Element_Size);
1428 Header_Fill_Code((int64u)-1, "Specific");
1429 return;
1430 }
1431
1432 //Parsing
1433 int8u nal_unit_type;
1434 if (!SizedBlocks)
1435 {
1436 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x00)
1437 Skip_B1( "zero_byte");
1438 Skip_B3( "start_code_prefix_one_3bytes");
1439 BS_Begin();
1440 Mark_0 ();
1441 Get_S1 ( 2, nal_ref_idc, "nal_ref_idc");
1442 Get_S1 ( 5, nal_unit_type, "nal_unit_type");
1443 BS_End();
1444 if (!Header_Parser_Fill_Size())
1445 {
1446 Element_WaitForMoreData();
1447 return;
1448 }
1449 }
1450 else
1451 {
1452 int32u Size;
1453 switch (SizeOfNALU_Minus1)
1454 {
1455 case 0: {
1456 int8u Size_;
1457 Get_B1 (Size_, "size");
1458 Size=Size_;
1459 }
1460 break;
1461 case 1: {
1462 int16u Size_;
1463 Get_B2 (Size_, "size");
1464 Size=Size_;
1465 }
1466 break;
1467 case 2: {
1468 int32u Size_;
1469 Get_B3 (Size_, "size");
1470 Size=Size_;
1471 }
1472 break;
1473 case 3: Get_B4 (Size, "size");
1474 break;
1475 default: Trusted_IsNot("No size of NALU defined");
1476 Size=(int32u)(Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset);
1477 }
1478 BS_Begin();
1479 Mark_0 ();
1480 Get_S1 ( 2, nal_ref_idc, "nal_ref_idc");
1481 Get_S1 ( 5, nal_unit_type, "nal_unit_type");
1482 BS_End();
1483
1484 FILLING_BEGIN();
1485 Header_Fill_Size(Size?(Element_Offset-1+Size):(Buffer_Size-Buffer_Offset)); //If Size is 0, it is not normal, we skip the complete frame
1486 FILLING_END();
1487 }
1488
1489 //Filling
1490 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1491 if (Trace_Activated)
1492 Header_Fill_Code(nal_unit_type, Ztring().From_CC1(nal_unit_type));
1493 else
1494 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1495 Header_Fill_Code(nal_unit_type);
1496}
1497
1498//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1499bool File_Avc::Header_Parser_Fill_Size()
1500{
1501 //Look for next Sync word
1502 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp==0) //Buffer_Offset_Temp is not 0 if Header_Parse_Fill_Size() has already parsed first frames
1503 Buffer_Offset_Temp=Buffer_Offset+4;
1504 while (Buffer_Offset_Temp+5<=Buffer_Size
1505 && CC3(Buffer+Buffer_Offset_Temp)!=0x000001)
1506 {
1507 Buffer_Offset_Temp+=2;
1508 while(Buffer_Offset_Temp<Buffer_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Temp]!=0x00)
1509 Buffer_Offset_Temp+=2;
1510 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp>=Buffer_Size || Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Temp-1]==0x00)
1511 Buffer_Offset_Temp--;
1512 }
1513
1514 //Must wait more data?
1515 if (Buffer_Offset_Temp+5>Buffer_Size)
1516 {
1517 if (FrameIsAlwaysComplete || File_Offset+Buffer_Size>=File_Size)
1518 Buffer_Offset_Temp=Buffer_Size; //We are sure that the next bytes are a start
1519 else
1520 return false;
1521 }
1522
1523 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset_Temp-1]==0x00)
1524 Buffer_Offset_Temp--;
1525
1526 //OK, we continue
1527 Header_Fill_Size(Buffer_Offset_Temp-Buffer_Offset);
1528 Buffer_Offset_Temp=0;
1529 return true;
1530}
1531
1532//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1533bool File_Avc::Header_Parser_QuickSearch()
1534{
1535 while ( Buffer_Offset+6<=Buffer_Size
1536 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset ]==0x00
1537 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+1]==0x00
1538 && (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x01
1539 || (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x00 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+3]==0x01)))
1540 {
1541 //Getting start_code
1542 int8u start_code;
1543 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+2]==0x00)
1544 start_code=CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+4)&0x1F;
1545 else
1546 start_code=CC1(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+3)&0x1F;
1547
1548 //Searching start
1549 if (Streams[start_code].Searching_Payload
1550 || Streams[start_code].ShouldDuplicate)
1551 return true;
1552
1553 //Synchronizing
1554 Buffer_Offset+=4;
1555 Synched=false;
1556 if (!Synchronize())
1557 {
1558 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=true;
1559 return false;
1560 }
1561
1562 if (Buffer_Offset+6>Buffer_Size)
1563 {
1564 UnSynched_IsNotJunk=true;
1565 return false;
1566 }
1567 }
1568
1569 Trusted_IsNot("AVC, Synchronisation lost");
1570 return Synchronize();
1571}
1572
1573//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1574void File_Avc::Data_Parse()
1575{
1576 //Specific case
1577 if (Element_Code==(int64u)-1)
1578 {
1579 SPS_PPS();
1580 return;
1581 }
1582
1583 //Trailing zeroes
1584 int64u Element_Size_SaveBeforeZeroes=Element_Size;
1585 if (Element_Size)
1586 {
1587 while (Element_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Size-1]==0)
1588 Element_Size--;
1589 }
1590
1591 //Dump of the SPS/PPS - Init
1592 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1593 size_t spspps_Size=0;
1594 if (true) //TODO: add an option for activating this extra piece of information in the output
1595 {
1596 switch (Element_Code)
1597 {
1598 case 0x07 : //seq_parameter_set();
1599 spspps_Size = seq_parameter_sets.size();
1600 break;
1601 case 0x08 : //pic_parameter_set();
1602 spspps_Size = pic_parameter_sets.size();
1603 break;
1604 default: ;
1605 }
1606 }
1607 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1608
1609 //svc_extension
1610 bool svc_extension_flag=false;
1611 if (Element_Code==0x0E || Element_Code==0x14)
1612 {
1613 BS_Begin();
1614 Get_SB (svc_extension_flag, "svc_extension_flag");
1615 if (svc_extension_flag)
1616 nal_unit_header_svc_extension();
1617 else
1618 nal_unit_header_mvc_extension();
1619 BS_End();
1620 }
1621
1622 //Searching emulation_prevention_three_byte
1623 int8u* Buffer_3Bytes=NULL;
1624 const int8u* Save_Buffer=Buffer;
1625 int64u Save_File_Offset=File_Offset;
1626 size_t Save_Buffer_Offset=Buffer_Offset;
1627 int64u Save_Element_Size=Element_Size;
1628 size_t Element_Offset_3Bytes=(size_t)Element_Offset;
1629 std::vector<size_t> ThreeByte_List;
1630 while (Element_Offset_3Bytes+3<=Element_Size)
1631 {
1632 if (CC3(Buffer+Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset_3Bytes)==0x000003)
1633 ThreeByte_List.push_back(Element_Offset_3Bytes+2);
1634 Element_Offset_3Bytes+=2;
1635 while(Element_Offset_3Bytes<Element_Size && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset_3Bytes]!=0x00)
1636 Element_Offset_3Bytes+=2;
1637 if (Element_Offset_3Bytes>=Element_Size || Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Element_Offset_3Bytes-1]==0x00)
1638 Element_Offset_3Bytes--;
1639 }
1640
1641 if (!ThreeByte_List.empty())
1642 {
1643 //We must change the buffer for keeping out
1644 Element_Size=Save_Element_Size-ThreeByte_List.size();
1645 File_Offset+=Buffer_Offset;
1646 Buffer_Offset=0;
1647 Buffer_3Bytes=new int8u[(size_t)Element_Size];
1648 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<=ThreeByte_List.size(); Pos++)
1649 {
1650 size_t Pos0=(Pos==ThreeByte_List.size())?(size_t)Save_Element_Size:(ThreeByte_List[Pos]);
1651 size_t Pos1=(Pos==0)?0:(ThreeByte_List[Pos-1]+1);
1652 size_t Buffer_3bytes_Begin=Pos1-Pos;
1653 size_t Save_Buffer_Begin =Pos1;
1654 size_t Size= Pos0-Pos1;
1655 std::memcpy(Buffer_3Bytes+Buffer_3bytes_Begin, Save_Buffer+Save_Buffer_Offset+Save_Buffer_Begin, Size);
1656 }
1657 Buffer=Buffer_3Bytes;
1658 }
1659
1660 //Parsing
1661 switch (Element_Code)
1662 {
1663 case 0x00 : Element_Name("unspecified"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1664 case 0x01 : slice_layer_without_partitioning_non_IDR(); break;
1665 case 0x02 : Element_Name("slice_data_partition_a_layer"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1666 case 0x03 : Element_Name("slice_data_partition_b_layer"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1667 case 0x04 : Element_Name("slice_data_partition_c_layer"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1668 case 0x05 : slice_layer_without_partitioning_IDR(); break;
1669 case 0x06 : sei(); break;
1670 case 0x07 : seq_parameter_set(); break;
1671 case 0x08 : pic_parameter_set(); break;
1672 case 0x09 : access_unit_delimiter(); break;
1673 case 0x0A : Element_Name("end_of_seq"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1674 case 0x0B : Element_Name("end_of_stream"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1675 case 0x0C : filler_data(); break;
1676 case 0x0D : Element_Name("seq_parameter_set_extension"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1677 case 0x0E : prefix_nal_unit(svc_extension_flag); break;
1678 case 0x0F : subset_seq_parameter_set(); break;
1679 case 0x13 : Element_Name("slice_layer_without_partitioning"); Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data"); break;
1680 case 0x14 : slice_layer_extension(svc_extension_flag); break;
1681 default :
1682 if (Element_Code<0x18)
1683 Element_Name("reserved");
1684 else
1685 Element_Name("unspecified");
1686 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Data");
1687 }
1688
1689 if (!ThreeByte_List.empty())
1690 {
1691 //We must change the buffer for keeping out
1692 Element_Size=Save_Element_Size;
1693 File_Offset=Save_File_Offset;
1694 Buffer_Offset=Save_Buffer_Offset;
1695 delete[] Buffer; Buffer=Save_Buffer;
1696 Buffer_3Bytes=NULL; //Same as Buffer...
1697 Element_Offset+=ThreeByte_List.size();
1698 }
1699
1700 //Duplicate
1701 #if MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1702 if (!Streams.empty() && Streams[(size_t)Element_Code].ShouldDuplicate)
1703 File__Duplicate_Write(Element_Code);
1704 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1705
1706 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1707 if (Demux_Avc_Transcode_Iso14496_15_to_Iso14496_10)
1708 {
1709 if (Element_Code==0x07)
1710 {
1711 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator Data_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin();
1712 if (Data_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end() && (*Data_Item))
1713 {
1714 delete[] (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer;
1715 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size=(size_t)(Element_Size+4);
1716 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer=new int8u[(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size];
1717 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[0]=0x00;
1718 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[1]=0x00;
1719 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[2]=0x01;
1720 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[3]=0x67;
1721 std::memcpy((*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer+4, Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size);
1722 }
1723 }
1724 if (Element_Code==0x08)
1725 {
1726 std::vector<pic_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator Data_Item=pic_parameter_sets.begin();
1727 if (Data_Item!=pic_parameter_sets.end() && (*Data_Item))
1728 {
1729 delete[] (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer;
1730 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size=(size_t)(Element_Size+4);
1731 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer=new int8u[(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size];
1732 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[0]=0x00;
1733 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[1]=0x00;
1734 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[2]=0x01;
1735 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[3]=0x68;
1736 std::memcpy((*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer+4, Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size);
1737 }
1738 }
1739 if (Element_Code==0x0F)
1740 {
1741 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator Data_Item=subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin();
1742 if (Data_Item!=subset_seq_parameter_sets.end() && (*Data_Item))
1743 {
1744 SizeOfNALU_Minus1=0;
1745 delete[] (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer;
1746 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size=(size_t)(Element_Size+4);
1747 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer=new int8u[(*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer_Size];
1748 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[0]=0x00;
1749 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[1]=0x00;
1750 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[2]=0x01;
1751 (*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer[3]=0x6F;
1752 std::memcpy((*Data_Item)->Iso14496_10_Buffer+4, Buffer+Buffer_Offset, (size_t)Element_Size);
1753 }
1754 }
1755 }
1756 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1757
1758 //Dump of the SPS/PPS - Fill
1759 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1760 if (false) //TODO: add an option for activating this extra piece of information in the output
1761 {
1762 switch (Element_Code)
1763 {
1764 case 0x07 : //seq_parameter_set();
1765 if (spspps_Size != seq_parameter_sets.size() && !Status[IsFilled])
1766 {
1767 std::string Data_Raw((const char*)(Buffer+(size_t)(Buffer_Offset-1)), (size_t)(Element_Size+1)); //Including the last byte in the header
1768 Dump_SPS.push_back(Base64::encode(Data_Raw));
1769 }
1770 break;
1771 case 0x08 : //pic_parameter_set();
1772 if (spspps_Size != pic_parameter_sets.size() && !Status[IsFilled])
1773 {
1774 std::string Data_Raw((const char*)(Buffer+(size_t)(Buffer_Offset-1)), (size_t)(Element_Size+1)); //Including the last byte in the header
1775 Dump_PPS.push_back(Base64::encode(Data_Raw));
1776 }
1777 break;
1778 default: ;
1779 }
1780 }
1781 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
1782
1783 //Trailing zeroes
1784 Element_Size=Element_Size_SaveBeforeZeroes;
1785}

1823//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1824//
1825void File_Avc::slice_header()
1826{
1827 //Encryption management
1828 if (CA_system_ID_MustSkipSlices)
1829 {
1830 //Is not decodable
1831 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data");
1832 Finish("AVC");
1833 return;
1834 }
1835
1836 Element_Begin1("slice_header");
1837
1838 //Parsing
1839 int32u slice_type, pic_order_cnt_lsb=(int32u)-1;
1840 int32u first_mb_in_slice, pic_parameter_set_id, frame_num, num_ref_idx_l0_active_minus1, num_ref_idx_l1_active_minus1, disable_deblocking_filter_idc, num_slice_groups_minus1, slice_group_map_type;
1841 int32s delta_pic_order_cnt_bottom=0;
1842 bool field_pic_flag=false, bottom_field_flag=false;
1843 Get_UE (first_mb_in_slice, "first_mb_in_slice");
1844 Get_UE (slice_type, "slice_type"); Param_Info1C((slice_type<10), Avc_slice_type[slice_type]);
1845 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
1846 {
1847 EVENT_BEGIN (Video, SliceInfo, 0)
1848 Event.FieldPosition=Field_Count;
1849 Event.SlicePosition=Element_IsOK()?first_mb_in_slice:(int64u)-1;
1850 switch (slice_type)
1851 {
1852 case 0 :
1853 case 3 :
1854 case 5 :
1855 case 8 :
1856 Event.SliceType=1; break;
1857 case 1 :
1858 case 6 :
1859 Event.SliceType=2; break;
1860 case 2 :
1861 case 4 :
1862 case 7 :
1863 case 9 :
1864 Event.SliceType=0; break;
1865 default:
1866 Event.SliceType=(int8u)-1;
1867 }
1868 Event.Flags=0;
1869 EVENT_END ()
1870 }
1871 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS
1872 if (slice_type>=10)
1873 {
1874 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data");
1875 Element_End0();
1876 return;
1877 }
1878 Get_UE (pic_parameter_set_id, "pic_parameter_set_id");
1879 std::vector<pic_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator pic_parameter_set_Item;
1880 if (pic_parameter_set_id>=pic_parameter_sets.size() || (*(pic_parameter_set_Item=pic_parameter_sets.begin()+pic_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
1881 {
1882 //Not yet present
1883 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data (pic_parameter_set is missing)");
1884 Element_End0();
1885 return;
1886 }
1887 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item;
1888 if ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->seq_parameter_set_id>=seq_parameter_sets.size() || (*(seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin()+(*pic_parameter_set_Item)->seq_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
1889 {
1890 if ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->seq_parameter_set_id>=subset_seq_parameter_sets.size() || (*(seq_parameter_set_Item=subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin()+(*pic_parameter_set_Item)->seq_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
1891 {
1892 //Not yet present
1893 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data (seq_parameter_set is missing)");
1894 Element_End0();
1895 return;
1896 }
1897 }
1898 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->separate_colour_plane_flag==1)
1899 Skip_S1(2, "color_plane_id");
1900 num_ref_idx_l0_active_minus1=(*pic_parameter_set_Item)->num_ref_idx_l0_default_active_minus1; //Default
1901 num_ref_idx_l1_active_minus1=(*pic_parameter_set_Item)->num_ref_idx_l1_default_active_minus1; //Default
1902 Get_BS ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->log2_max_frame_num_minus4+4, frame_num, "frame_num");
1903 if (!(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag)
1904 {
1905 TEST_SB_GET(field_pic_flag, "field_pic_flag");
1906 Get_SB (bottom_field_flag, "bottom_field_flag");
1907 TEST_SB_END();
1908 }
1909 if (Element_Code==5) //IdrPicFlag
1910 Skip_UE( "idr_pic_id");
1911 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==0)
1912 {
1913 Get_BS ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4+4, pic_order_cnt_lsb, "pic_order_cnt_lsb");
1914 if ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->bottom_field_pic_order_in_frame_present_flag && !field_pic_flag)
1915 Get_SE (delta_pic_order_cnt_bottom, "delta_pic_order_cnt_bottom");
1916 }
1917 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==1 && !(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->delta_pic_order_always_zero_flag )
1918 {
1919 Skip_SE( "delta_pic_order_cnt[0]");
1920 if((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->bottom_field_pic_order_in_frame_present_flag && !field_pic_flag)
1921 Skip_SE( "delta_pic_order_cnt[1]");
1922 }
1923 if((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->redundant_pic_cnt_present_flag)
1924 Skip_UE( "redundant_pic_cnt");
1925 if (slice_type==1 || slice_type==6) //B-Frame
1926 Skip_SB( "direct_spatial_mv_pred_flag");
1927 switch (slice_type)
1928 {
1929 case 0 : //P-Frame
1930 case 1 : //B-Frame
1931 case 3 : //SP-Frame
1932 case 5 : //P-Frame
1933 case 6 : //B-Frame
1934 case 8 : //SP-Frame
1935 TEST_SB_SKIP( "num_ref_idx_active_override_flag");
1936 Get_UE (num_ref_idx_l0_active_minus1, "num_ref_idx_l0_active_minus1");
1937 switch (slice_type)
1938 {
1939 case 1 : //B-Frame
1940 case 6 : //B-Frame
1941 Get_UE (num_ref_idx_l1_active_minus1, "num_ref_idx_l1_active_minus1");
1942 break;
1943 default: ;
1944 }
1945 TEST_SB_END();
1946 break;
1947 default: ;
1948 }
1949 ref_pic_list_modification(slice_type, Element_Code==20); //nal_unit_type==20 --> ref_pic_list_mvc_modification()
1950 if (((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->weighted_pred_flag && (slice_type==0 || slice_type==3 || slice_type==5 || slice_type==8))
1951 || ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->weighted_bipred_idc==1 && (slice_type==1 || slice_type==6)))
1952 pred_weight_table(num_ref_idx_l0_active_minus1, num_ref_idx_l1_active_minus1, (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->ChromaArrayType());
1953 std::vector<int8u> memory_management_control_operations;
1954 if (nal_ref_idc)
1955 dec_ref_pic_marking(memory_management_control_operations);
1956
1957 if ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->entropy_coding_mode_flag &&
1958 (slice_type!=2 && slice_type!=7 && //I-Frames
1959 slice_type!=4 && slice_type!=9)) //SI-Frames
1960 Skip_UE( "cabac_init_idc");
1961 Skip_SE( "slice_qp_delta");
1962 switch (slice_type)
1963 {
1964 case 3 : //SP-Frame
1965 case 4 : //SI-Frame
1966 case 8 : //SP-Frame
1967 case 9 : //SI-Frame
1968 switch (slice_type)
1969 {
1970 case 3 : //SP-Frame
1971 case 8 : //SP-Frame
1972 Skip_SB( "sp_for_switch_flag");
1973 break;
1974 default: ;
1975 }
1976 Skip_SE ( "slice_qs_delta");
1977 break;
1978 default: ;
1979 }
1980 if ((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->deblocking_filter_control_present_flag)
1981 {
1982 Get_UE(disable_deblocking_filter_idc, "disable_deblocking_filter_idc");
1983 if (disable_deblocking_filter_idc!=1)
1984 {
1985 Skip_SE( "slice_alpha_c0_offset_div2");
1986 Skip_SE( "slice_beta_offset_div2");
1987 }
1988 }
1989 num_slice_groups_minus1=(*pic_parameter_set_Item)->num_slice_groups_minus1; //Default
1990 slice_group_map_type=(*pic_parameter_set_Item)->slice_group_map_type; //Default
1991 //if (num_slice_groups_minus1 > 0 && slice_group_map_type >=3 && slice_group_map_type <=5)
1992 // Get_BS ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->log2_max_slice_group_change_cycle_minus4+4, slice_group_change_cycle, "slice_group_change_cycle");
1993
1994 Element_End0();
1995
1996 FILLING_BEGIN();
1997 //Count of I-Frames
1998 if (first_mb_in_slice==0 && Element_Code!=20 && (slice_type==2 || slice_type==7)) //Not slice_layer_extension, I-Frame
1999 IFrame_Count++;
2000
2001 //pic_struct
2002 if (field_pic_flag && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_struct_FirstDetected==(int8u)-1)
2003 (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_struct_FirstDetected=bottom_field_flag?2:1; //2=BFF, 1=TFF
2004
2005 //Saving some info
2006 int32s TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Diff=0;
2007 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type!=1 && first_mb_in_slice==0 && (Element_Code!=0x14 || seq_parameter_sets.empty())) //Not slice_layer_extension except if MVC only
2008 {
2009 if (field_pic_flag)
2010 {
2011 Structure_Field++;
2012 if (bottom_field_flag)
2013 Interlaced_Bottom++;
2014 else
2015 Interlaced_Top++;
2016 }
2017 else
2018 Structure_Frame++;
2019
2020 //Frame order detection
2021 int64s pic_order_cnt=0;
2022 switch ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type)
2023 {
2024 case 0 :
2025 {
2026 if (Element_Code==5) //IDR
2027 {
2028 prevPicOrderCntMsb=0;
2029 prevPicOrderCntLsb=0;
2030 TemporalReferences_Offset=TemporalReferences_Max;
2031 if (TemporalReferences_Offset%2)
2032 TemporalReferences_Offset++;
2033 TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min=0;
2034 }
2035 else
2036 {
2037 bool Has5=false;
2038 for (std::vector<int8u>::iterator Temp=memory_management_control_operations.begin(); Temp!=memory_management_control_operations.end(); ++Temp)
2039 if ((*Temp)==5)
2040 {
2041 Has5=true;
2042 break;
2043 }
2044 if (Has5)
2045 {
2046 prevPicOrderCntMsb=0;
2047 if (bottom_field_flag)
2048 prevPicOrderCntLsb=0;
2049 else
2050 prevPicOrderCntLsb=prevTopFieldOrderCnt;
2051 }
2052 }
2053 int32s PicOrderCntMsb;
2054 if (prevPicOrderCntLsb==(int32u)-1)
2055 {
2056 PicOrderCntMsb=0;
2057 if ((int32u)(2*((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames+3))<pic_order_cnt_lsb)
2058 TemporalReferences_Min=pic_order_cnt_lsb-2*((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->max_num_ref_frames+3);
2059 }
2060 else if (pic_order_cnt_lsb<prevPicOrderCntLsb && prevPicOrderCntLsb-pic_order_cnt_lsb>=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxPicOrderCntLsb/2)
2061 PicOrderCntMsb=prevPicOrderCntMsb+(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxPicOrderCntLsb;
2062 else if (pic_order_cnt_lsb>prevPicOrderCntLsb && pic_order_cnt_lsb-prevPicOrderCntLsb>(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxPicOrderCntLsb/2)
2063 PicOrderCntMsb=prevPicOrderCntMsb-(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxPicOrderCntLsb;
2064 else
2065 PicOrderCntMsb=prevPicOrderCntMsb;
2066
2067 int32s TopFieldOrderCnt=PicOrderCntMsb+pic_order_cnt_lsb;
2068 int32s BottomFieldOrderCnt;
2069 if (field_pic_flag)
2070 BottomFieldOrderCnt=TopFieldOrderCnt+delta_pic_order_cnt_bottom;
2071 else
2072 BottomFieldOrderCnt=PicOrderCntMsb+pic_order_cnt_lsb;
2073
2074 prevPicOrderCntMsb=PicOrderCntMsb;
2075 prevPicOrderCntLsb=pic_order_cnt_lsb;
2076 prevTopFieldOrderCnt=TopFieldOrderCnt;
2077
2078 pic_order_cnt=bottom_field_flag?BottomFieldOrderCnt:TopFieldOrderCnt;
2079 }
2080 break;
2081 case 2 :
2082 {
2083 bool Has5=false;
2084 for (std::vector<int8u>::iterator Temp=memory_management_control_operations.begin(); Temp!=memory_management_control_operations.end(); ++Temp)
2085 if ((*Temp)==5)
2086 {
2087 Has5=true;
2088 break;
2089 }
2090 if (Has5)
2091 prevFrameNumOffset=0;
2092 int32u FrameNumOffset;
2093
2094 if (Element_Code==5) //IdrPicFlag
2095 {
2096 TemporalReferences_Offset=TemporalReferences_Max;
2097 if (TemporalReferences_Offset%2)
2098 TemporalReferences_Offset++;
2099 FrameNumOffset=0;
2100 }
2101 else if (prevFrameNumOffset==(int32u)-1)
2102 FrameNumOffset=0;
2103 else if (prevFrameNum>frame_num)
2104 FrameNumOffset=prevFrameNumOffset+(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->MaxFrameNum;
2105 else
2106 FrameNumOffset=prevFrameNumOffset;
2107
2108 int32u tempPicOrderCnt;
2109 if (Element_Code==5) //IdrPicFlag
2110 tempPicOrderCnt=0;
2111 else
2112 {
2113 tempPicOrderCnt=2*(FrameNumOffset+frame_num);
2114 if (!nal_ref_idc && tempPicOrderCnt) //Note: if nal_ref_idc is 0, tempPicOrderCnt is not expected to be 0 but it may be the case with invalid streams
2115 tempPicOrderCnt--;
2116 }
2117
2118 pic_order_cnt=tempPicOrderCnt;
2119
2120 prevFrameNum=frame_num;
2121 prevFrameNumOffset=FrameNumOffset;
2122
2123 pic_order_cnt_lsb=frame_num;
2124 }
2125 break;
2126 default: ;
2127 }
2128
2129 if (pic_order_cnt<TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min)
2130 {
2131 if (pic_order_cnt<0)
2132 {
2133 size_t Base=(size_t)(TemporalReferences_Offset+TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min);
2134 size_t ToInsert=(size_t)(TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min-pic_order_cnt);
2135 if (Base+ToInsert>=4*TemporalReferences_Reserved || Base>=4*TemporalReferences_Reserved || ToInsert+TemporalReferences_Max>=4*TemporalReferences_Reserved || TemporalReferences_Max>=4*TemporalReferences_Reserved || TemporalReferences_Max-Base>=4*TemporalReferences_Reserved)
2136 {
2137 Trusted_IsNot("Problem in temporal references");
2138 return;
2139 }
2140 Element_Info1(__T("Offset of ")+Ztring::ToZtring(ToInsert));
2141 TemporalReferences.insert(TemporalReferences.begin()+Base, ToInsert, NULL);
2142 TemporalReferences_Offset+=ToInsert;
2143 TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last += ToInsert;
2144 TemporalReferences_Max+=ToInsert;
2145 TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min=pic_order_cnt;
2146 }
2147 else if (TemporalReferences_Min>(size_t)(TemporalReferences_Offset+pic_order_cnt))
2148 TemporalReferences_Min=(size_t)(TemporalReferences_Offset+pic_order_cnt);
2149 }
2150
2151 if (pic_order_cnt<0 && TemporalReferences_Offset<(size_t)(-pic_order_cnt)) //Found in playreadyEncryptedBlowUp.ts without encryption test
2152 {
2153 Trusted_IsNot("Problem in temporal references");
2154 return;
2155 }
2156
2157 if ((size_t)(TemporalReferences_Offset+pic_order_cnt)>=3*TemporalReferences_Reserved)
2158 {
2159 size_t Offset=TemporalReferences_Max-TemporalReferences_Offset;
2160 if (Offset%2)
2161 Offset++;
2162 if (Offset>=TemporalReferences_Reserved && pic_order_cnt>=(int64s)TemporalReferences_Reserved)
2163 {
2164 TemporalReferences_Offset+=TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2165 pic_order_cnt-=TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2166 TemporalReferences_pic_order_cnt_Min-=TemporalReferences_Reserved/2;
2167 switch ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type)
2168 {
2169 case 0 :
2170 prevPicOrderCntMsb-=(int32u)TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2171 break;
2172 case 2 :
2173 prevFrameNumOffset-=(int32u)TemporalReferences_Reserved/2;
2174 break;
2175 default:;
2176 }
2177 }
2178 while (TemporalReferences_Offset+pic_order_cnt>=3*TemporalReferences_Reserved)
2179 {
2180 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReferences_Reserved; Pos++)
2181 {
2182 if (TemporalReferences[Pos])
2183 {
2184 if ((Pos%2)==0)
2185 PictureTypes_PreviousFrames+=Avc_slice_type[TemporalReferences[Pos]->slice_type];
2186 }
2187 else if (!PictureTypes_PreviousFrames.empty()) //Only if stream already started
2188 {
2189 if ((Pos%2)==0)
2190 PictureTypes_PreviousFrames+=' ';
2191 }
2192 delete TemporalReferences[Pos];
2193 }
2194 if (PictureTypes_PreviousFrames.size()>=8*TemporalReferences.size())
2195 PictureTypes_PreviousFrames.erase(PictureTypes_PreviousFrames.begin(), PictureTypes_PreviousFrames.begin()+PictureTypes_PreviousFrames.size()-TemporalReferences.size());
2196 TemporalReferences.erase(TemporalReferences.begin(), TemporalReferences.begin()+TemporalReferences_Reserved);
2197 TemporalReferences.resize(4*TemporalReferences_Reserved);
2198 if (TemporalReferences_Reserved<TemporalReferences_Offset)
2199 TemporalReferences_Offset-=TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2200 else
2201 TemporalReferences_Offset=0;
2202 if (TemporalReferences_Reserved<TemporalReferences_Min)
2203 TemporalReferences_Min-=TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2204 else
2205 TemporalReferences_Min=0;
2206 if (TemporalReferences_Reserved<TemporalReferences_Max)
2207 TemporalReferences_Max-=TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2208 else
2209 TemporalReferences_Max=0;
2210 if (TemporalReferences_Reserved<TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last)
2211 TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last-=TemporalReferences_Reserved;
2212 else
2213 TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last=0;
2214 }
2215 }
2216
2217 TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Diff=(int32s)((int32s)(TemporalReferences_Offset+pic_order_cnt)-TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last);
2218 TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last=(size_t)(TemporalReferences_Offset+pic_order_cnt);
2219 if (TemporalReferences_Max<=TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last)
2220 TemporalReferences_Max=TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last+((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag?2:1);
2221 if (TemporalReferences_Min>TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last)
2222 TemporalReferences_Min=TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last;
2223 if (TemporalReferences_DelayedElement)
2224 {
2225 delete TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]; TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]=TemporalReferences_DelayedElement;
2226 }
2227 if (TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]==NULL)
2228 TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]=new temporal_reference();
2229 TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]->frame_num=frame_num;
2230 TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]->slice_type=(int8u)slice_type;
2231 TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]->IsTop=!bottom_field_flag;
2232 TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last]->IsField=field_pic_flag;
2233 if (TemporalReferences_DelayedElement)
2234 {
2235 TemporalReferences_DelayedElement=NULL;
2236 sei_message_user_data_registered_itu_t_t35_GA94_03_Delayed((*pic_parameter_set_Item)->seq_parameter_set_id);
2237 }
2238 }
2239
2240 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->timing_info_present_flag && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->num_units_in_tick)
2241 tc=float64_int64s(((float64)1000000000)/((float64)(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->time_scale/(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->num_units_in_tick/((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==2?1:2)/FrameRate_Divider)/((!(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag && field_pic_flag)?2:1));
2242 if (first_mb_in_slice==0)
2243 {
2244 if (Frame_Count==0)
2245 {
2246 if (FrameInfo.PTS==(int64u)-1)
2247 FrameInfo.PTS=FrameInfo.DTS+tc*(TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Diff?2:1)*((!(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag && field_pic_flag)?2:1); //No PTS in container
2248 PTS_Begin=FrameInfo.PTS;
2249 }
2250 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
2251 if (PTS_Begin_Segment==(int64u)-1 && File_Offset>=Config->File_Current_Offset)
2252 {
2253 PTS_Begin_Segment=FrameInfo.PTS;
2254 }
2255 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED2
2256 if (slice_type==2 || slice_type==7) //IFrame
2257 FirstPFrameInGop_IsParsed=false;
2258 }
2259 else
2260 {
2261 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1)
2262 FrameInfo.PTS-=tc;
2263 if (FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2264 FrameInfo.DTS-=tc;
2265 }
2266
2267 //Frame pos
2268 if (Frame_Count!=(int64u)-1 && Frame_Count && ((!(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag && Interlaced_Top==Interlaced_Bottom && field_pic_flag) || first_mb_in_slice!=0 || (Element_Code==0x14 && !seq_parameter_sets.empty())))
2269 {
2270 Frame_Count--;
2271 if (IFrame_Count && Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
2272 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded--;
2273 Frame_Count_InThisBlock--;
2274 }
2275 else if (first_mb_in_slice==0)
2276 {
2277 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type!=1 && (Element_Code!=0x14 || seq_parameter_sets.empty())) //Not slice_layer_extension except if MVC only
2278 {
2279 if ((!IsSub || Frame_Count_InThisBlock) && TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Diff && TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Diff!=2)
2280 FrameInfo.PTS+=(TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Diff-(field_pic_flag?1:2))/((!(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag && field_pic_flag)?1:2)*(int64s)tc;
2281 }
2282
2283 if (!FirstPFrameInGop_IsParsed && (slice_type==0 || slice_type==5)) //P-Frame
2284 {
2285 FirstPFrameInGop_IsParsed=true;
2286
2287 //Testing if we have enough to test GOP
2288 if (Frame_Count<=Frame_Count_Valid)
2289 {
2290 std::string PictureTypes(PictureTypes_PreviousFrames);
2291 PictureTypes.reserve(TemporalReferences.size());
2292 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<TemporalReferences.size(); Pos++)
2293 if (TemporalReferences[Pos])
2294 {
2295 if ((Pos%2)==0)
2296 PictureTypes+=Avc_slice_type[TemporalReferences[Pos]->slice_type];
2297 }
2298 else if (!PictureTypes.empty()) //Only if stream already started
2299 {
2300 if ((Pos%2)==0)
2301 PictureTypes+=' ';
2302 }
2303 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
2304 if (!GOP_Detect(PictureTypes).empty() && !GA94_03_IsPresent)
2305 Frame_Count_Valid=Frame_Count; //We have enough frames
2306 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
2307 }
2308 }
2309 }
2310
2311 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2312 if (Trace_Activated)
2313 {
2314 Element_Info1(TemporalReferences_Offset_pic_order_cnt_lsb_Last);
2315 Element_Info1((((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag || !field_pic_flag)?__T("Frame "):(bottom_field_flag?__T("Field (Bottom) "):__T("Field (Top) ")))+Ztring::ToZtring(Frame_Count));
2316 if (slice_type<9)
2317 Element_Info1(__T("slice_type ")+Ztring().From_Local(Avc_slice_type[slice_type]));
2318 Element_Info1(__T("frame_num ")+Ztring::ToZtring(frame_num));
2319 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->fixed_frame_rate_flag)
2320 {
2321 if (FrameInfo.PCR!=(int64u)-1)
2322 Element_Info1(__T("PCR ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.PCR)/1000000)));
2323 if (FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2324 Element_Info1(__T("DTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.DTS)/1000000)));
2325 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1)
2326 Element_Info1(__T("PTS ")+Ztring().Duration_From_Milliseconds(float64_int64s(((float64)FrameInfo.PTS)/1000000)));
2327 }
2328 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==0)
2329 Element_Info1(__T("pic_order_cnt_lsb ")+Ztring::ToZtring(pic_order_cnt_lsb));
2330 if (first_mb_in_slice)
2331 Element_Info1(__T("first_mb_in_slice ")+Ztring::ToZtring(first_mb_in_slice));
2332 }
2333 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
2334
2335 //Counting
2336 if (Frame_Count!=(int64u)-1)
2337 {
2338 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Size==File_Size)
2339 Frame_Count_Valid=Frame_Count; //Finish frames in case of there are less than Frame_Count_Valid frames
2340 Frame_Count++;
2341 if (IFrame_Count && Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded!=(int64u)-1)
2342 Frame_Count_NotParsedIncluded++;
2343 Frame_Count_InThisBlock++;
2344 }
2345 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==0 && field_pic_flag)
2346 {
2347 Field_Count++;
2348 Field_Count_InThisBlock++;
2349 }
2350 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1)
2351 FrameInfo.PTS+=tc;
2352 if (FrameInfo.DTS!=(int64u)-1)
2353 FrameInfo.DTS+=tc;
2354 if (FrameInfo.PTS!=(int64u)-1 && (FrameInfo.PTS>PTS_End || (PTS_End>1000000000 && FrameInfo.PTS<=PTS_End-1000000000))) //More than current PTS_End or less than current PTS_End minus 1 second (there is a problem?)
2355 PTS_End=FrameInfo.PTS;
2356
2357 #if MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
2358 if (Streams[(size_t)Element_Code].ShouldDuplicate)
2359 File__Duplicate_Write(Element_Code, (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_order_cnt_type==0?pic_order_cnt_lsb:frame_num);
2360 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
2361
2362 //Filling only if not already done
2363 if (Frame_Count==1 && !Status[IsAccepted])
2364 Accept("AVC");
2365 if (!Status[IsFilled])
2366 {
2367 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
2368 if (!GA94_03_IsPresent && IFrame_Count>=8)
2369 Frame_Count_Valid=Frame_Count; //We have enough frames
2370 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
2371 if (Frame_Count>=Frame_Count_Valid)
2372 {
2373 Fill("AVC");
2374 if (!IsSub && !Streams[(size_t)Element_Code].ShouldDuplicate && MediaInfoLib::Config.ParseSpeed_Get()<1.0)
2375 Finish("AVC");
2376 }
2377 }
2378 FILLING_END();
2379}

2400 do

2417 }
2418 if ((slice_type%5)==1)
2419 {
2420 TEST_SB_SKIP( "ref_pic_list_modification_flag_l1");
2421 int32u modification_of_pic_nums_idc;
2422 do
2423 {
2424 Get_UE (modification_of_pic_nums_idc, "modification_of_pic_nums_idc");
2425 if (modification_of_pic_nums_idc<2)
2426 Skip_UE( "abs_diff_pic_num_minus1");
2427 else if (modification_of_pic_nums_idc==2)
2428 Skip_UE( "long_term_pic_num");
2429 else if (mvc && (modification_of_pic_nums_idc==4 || modification_of_pic_nums_idc==5)) //ref_pic_list_mvc_modification only
2430 Skip_UE( "abs_diff_view_idx_minus1");
2431 else if (modification_of_pic_nums_idc!=3)
2432 {
2433 Trusted_IsNot("ref_pic_list_modification_flag_l1");
2434 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "(Remaining bits)");

2506//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2507// Packet "06"
2508void File_Avc::sei()
2509{
2510 Element_Name("sei");
2511
2512 //Parsing
2513 int32u seq_parameter_set_id=(int32u)-1;
2514 while(Element_Offset+1<Element_Size)
2515 {
2516 Element_Begin1("sei message");
2517 sei_message(seq_parameter_set_id);
2518 Element_End0();
2519 }
2520 BS_Begin();
2521 Mark_1( );
2522 BS_End();
2523}
2524
2525//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2526void File_Avc::sei_message(int32u &seq_parameter_set_id)
2527{
2528 //Parsing
2529 int32u payloadType=0, payloadSize=0;
2530 int8u payload_type_byte, payload_size_byte;
2531 Element_Begin1("sei message header");
2532 do
2533 {
2534 Get_B1 (payload_type_byte, "payload_type_byte");
2535 payloadType+=payload_type_byte;
2536 }
2537 while(payload_type_byte==0xFF);
2538 do
2539 {
2540 Get_B1 (payload_size_byte, "payload_size_byte");
2541 payloadSize+=payload_size_byte;
2542 }
2543 while(payload_size_byte==0xFF);
2544 Element_End0();
2545
2546 int64u Element_Offset_Save=Element_Offset+payloadSize;
2547 if (Element_Offset_Save>Element_Size)
2548 {
2549 Trusted_IsNot("Wrong size");
2550 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "unknown");
2551 return;
2552 }
2553 int64u Element_Size_Save=Element_Size;
2554 Element_Size=Element_Offset_Save;
2555 switch (payloadType)
2556 {
2557 case 0 : sei_message_buffering_period(seq_parameter_set_id); break;
2558 case 1 : sei_message_pic_timing(payloadSize, seq_parameter_set_id); break;
2559 case 4 : sei_message_user_data_registered_itu_t_t35(); break;
2560 case 5 : sei_message_user_data_unregistered(payloadSize); break;
2561 case 6 : sei_message_recovery_point(); break;
2562 case 32 : sei_message_mainconcept(payloadSize); break;
2563 default :
2564 Element_Info1("unknown");
2565 Skip_XX(payloadSize, "data");
2566 }
2567 Element_Offset=Element_Offset_Save; //Positionning in the right place.
2568 Element_Size=Element_Size_Save; //Positionning in the right place.
2569}
2570

2572// SEI - 0
2573void File_Avc::sei_message_buffering_period(int32u &seq_parameter_set_id)
2574{
2575 Element_Info1("buffering_period");
2576
2577 //Parsing
2578 if (Element_Offset==Element_Size)
2579 return; //Nothing to do
2580 BS_Begin();
2581 Get_UE (seq_parameter_set_id, "seq_parameter_set_id");
2582 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item;
2583 if (seq_parameter_set_id>=seq_parameter_sets.size() || (*(seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin()+seq_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
2584 {
2585 //Not yet present
2586 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data (seq_parameter_set is missing)");
2587 BS_End();
2588 return;
2589 }
2590 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->NalHrdBpPresentFlag())
2591 sei_message_buffering_period_xxl((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL);
2592 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->VclHrdBpPresentFlag())
2593 sei_message_buffering_period_xxl((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->VCL);
2594 BS_End();
2595}

2598{
