2610//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2611// SEI - 1
2612void File_Avc::sei_message_pic_timing(int32u /*payloadSize*/, int32u seq_parameter_set_id)
2613{
2614 Element_Info1("pic_timing");
2615
2616 //Testing if we can parsing it now. TODO: handle case seq_parameter_set_id is unknown (buffering of message, decoding in slice parsing)
2617 if (seq_parameter_set_id==(int32u)-1 && seq_parameter_sets.size()==1)
2618 seq_parameter_set_id=0;
2619 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item;
2620 if (seq_parameter_set_id>=seq_parameter_sets.size() || (*(seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin()+seq_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
2621 {
2622 //Not yet present
2623 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data (seq_parameter_set is missing)");
2624 return;
2625 }
2626
2627 //Parsing
2628 int8u pic_struct=(int8u)-1;
2629 BS_Begin();
2630 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->CpbDpbDelaysPresentFlag())
2631 {
2632 int8u cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL?(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL->cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1:(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->VCL->cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1; //Spec is not precise, I am not sure
2633 int8u dpb_output_delay_length_minus1=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL?(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL->dpb_output_delay_length_minus1:(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->VCL->dpb_output_delay_length_minus1; //Spec is not precise, I am not sure
2634 Skip_S4(cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1+1, "cpb_removal_delay");
2635 Skip_S4(dpb_output_delay_length_minus1+1, "dpb_output_delay");
2636 }
2637 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->pic_struct_present_flag)
2638 {
2639 Get_S1 (4, pic_struct, "pic_struct");
2640 switch (pic_struct)
2641 {
2642 case 0 :
2643 case 1 :
2644 case 2 :
2645 case 3 :
2646 case 4 :
2647 case 5 :
2648 case 6 : break;
2649 case 7 : FrameRate_Divider=2; break;
2650 case 8 : FrameRate_Divider=3; break;
2651 default : Param_Info1("Reserved"); return; //NumClockTS is unknown
2652 }
2653 Param_Info1(Avc_pic_struct[pic_struct]);
2654 int8u NumClockTS=Avc_NumClockTS[pic_struct];
2655 int8u seconds_value=0, minutes_value=0, hours_value=0; //Here because theses values can be reused in later ClockTSs.
2656 for (int8u i=0; i<NumClockTS; i++)
2657 {
2658 Element_Begin1("ClockTS");
2659 TEST_SB_SKIP( "clock_timestamp_flag");
2660 Ztring TimeStamp;
2661 int32u time_offset=0;
2662 int8u n_frames;
2663 bool full_timestamp_flag, nuit_field_based_flag;
2664 Info_S1(2, ct_type, "ct_type"); Param_Info1(Avc_ct_type[ct_type]);
2665 Get_SB ( nuit_field_based_flag, "nuit_field_based_flag");
2666 Skip_S1(5, "counting_type");
2667 Get_SB ( full_timestamp_flag, "full_timestamp_flag");
2668 Skip_SB( "discontinuity_flag");
2669 Skip_SB( "cnt_dropped_flag");
2670 Get_S1 (8, n_frames, "n_frames");
2671 if (full_timestamp_flag)
2672 {
2673 Get_S1 (6, seconds_value, "seconds_value");
2674 Get_S1 (6, minutes_value, "minutes_value");
2675 Get_S1 (5, hours_value, "hours_value");
2676 }
2677 else
2678 {
2679 TEST_SB_SKIP( "seconds_flag");
2680 Get_S1 (6, seconds_value, "seconds_value");
2681 TEST_SB_SKIP( "minutes_flag");
2682 Get_S1 (6, minutes_value, "minutes_value");
2683 TEST_SB_SKIP( "hours_flag");
2684 Get_S1 (5, hours_value, "hours_value");
2685 TEST_SB_END();
2686 TEST_SB_END();
2687 TEST_SB_END();
2688 }
2689 TimeStamp=Ztring::ToZtring(hours_value)+__T(':')+Ztring::ToZtring(minutes_value)+__T(':')+Ztring::ToZtring(seconds_value);
2690 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->CpbDpbDelaysPresentFlag())
2691 {
2692 int8u time_offset_length=(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL?(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->NAL->time_offset_length:(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->VCL->time_offset_length; //Spec is not precise, I am not sure
2693 if (time_offset_length)
2694 Get_S4 (time_offset_length, time_offset, "time_offset");
2695 }
2696 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->timing_info_present_flag && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->time_scale)
2697 {
2698 float32 Milliseconds=((float32)(n_frames*((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->num_units_in_tick*(1+(nuit_field_based_flag?1:0)))+time_offset))/(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->time_scale;
2699 TimeStamp+=__T('.');
2700 TimeStamp+=Ztring::ToZtring(Milliseconds);
2701 }
2702 Element_Info1(TimeStamp);
2703 TEST_SB_END();
2704 Element_End0();
2705 }
2706 }
2707 BS_End();
2708
2709 FILLING_BEGIN();
2710 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_struct_FirstDetected==(int8u)-1 && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->pic_struct_present_flag)
2711 (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_struct_FirstDetected=pic_struct;
2712 FILLING_END();
2713}

2826void File_Avc::sei_message_user_data_registered_itu_t_t35_GA94_03_Delayed(int32u seq_parameter_set_id)
2827{
2828 // Skipping missing frames
2829 if (TemporalReferences_Max-TemporalReferences_Min>(size_t)(4*(seq_parameter_sets[seq_parameter_set_id]->max_num_ref_frames+3))) // max_num_ref_frames ref frame maximum
2830 {
2831 TemporalReferences_Min=TemporalReferences_Max-4*(seq_parameter_sets[seq_parameter_set_id]->max_num_ref_frames+3);
2832 while (TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]==NULL)
2833 TemporalReferences_Min++;
2834 }
2835
2836 // Parsing captions
2837 while (TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min] && TemporalReferences_Min+2*seq_parameter_sets[seq_parameter_set_id]->max_num_ref_frames<TemporalReferences_Max)
2838 {
2839 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
2840 Element_Begin1("Reordered DTVCC Transport");
2841
2842 //Parsing
2843 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2844 int64u Element_Code_Old=Element_Code;
2845 Element_Code=0x4741393400000003LL;
2846 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2847 if (GA94_03_Parser==NULL)
2848 {
2849 GA94_03_Parser=new File_DtvccTransport;
2850 Open_Buffer_Init(GA94_03_Parser);
2851 ((File_DtvccTransport*)GA94_03_Parser)->Format=File_DtvccTransport::Format_A53_4_GA94_03;
2852 }
2853 if (((File_DtvccTransport*)GA94_03_Parser)->AspectRatio==0)
2854 {
2855 float64 PixelAspectRatio=1;
2856 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin();
2857 for (; seq_parameter_set_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end(); ++seq_parameter_set_Item)
2858 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item))
2859 break;
2860 if (seq_parameter_set_Item!=seq_parameter_sets.end())
2861 {
2862 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_info_present_flag)
2863 {
2864 if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_idc<Avc_PixelAspectRatio_Size)
2865 PixelAspectRatio=Avc_PixelAspectRatio[(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_idc];
2866 else if ((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->aspect_ratio_idc==0xFF && (*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->sar_height)
2867 PixelAspectRatio=((float64)(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->sar_width)/(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->vui_parameters->sar_height;
2868 }
2869 int32u Width =((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_width_in_mbs_minus1 +1)*16;
2870 int32u Height=((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_height_in_map_units_minus1+1)*16*(2-(*seq_parameter_set_Item)->frame_mbs_only_flag);
2871 ((File_DtvccTransport*)GA94_03_Parser)->AspectRatio=Width*PixelAspectRatio/Height;
2872 }
2873 }
2874 if (GA94_03_Parser->PTS_DTS_Needed)
2875 {
2876 GA94_03_Parser->FrameInfo.PCR=FrameInfo.PCR;
2877 GA94_03_Parser->FrameInfo.PTS=FrameInfo.PTS;
2878 GA94_03_Parser->FrameInfo.DTS=FrameInfo.DTS;
2879 }
2880 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2881 if (TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->GA94_03)
2882 {
2883 int8u Demux_Level_Save=Demux_Level;
2884 Demux_Level=8; //Ancillary
2885 Demux(TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->GA94_03->Data, TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->GA94_03->Size, ContentType_MainStream);
2886 Demux_Level=Demux_Level_Save;
2887 }
2888 Element_Code=Element_Code_Old;
2889 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
2890 if (TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->GA94_03)
2891 {
2892 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_EIA608_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_EIA708_YES)
2893 GA94_03_Parser->ServiceDescriptors=ServiceDescriptors;
2894 #endif
2895 Open_Buffer_Continue(GA94_03_Parser, TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->GA94_03->Data, TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->GA94_03->Size);
2896 }
2897
2898 Element_End0();
2899 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_DTVCCTRANSPORT_YES)
2900
2901 TemporalReferences_Min+=((seq_parameter_sets[seq_parameter_set_id]->frame_mbs_only_flag | !TemporalReferences[TemporalReferences_Min]->IsField)?2:1);
2902 }
2903}

2985//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2986// SEI - 5 - x264
2987void File_Avc::sei_message_user_data_unregistered_x264(int32u payloadSize)
2988{
2989 //Parsing
2990 Ztring Data;
2991 Peek_Local(payloadSize, Data);
2992 if (Data.size()!=payloadSize && Data.size()+1!=payloadSize)
2993 {
2994 Skip_XX(payloadSize, "Unknown");
2995 return; //This is not a text string
2996 }
2997 size_t Data_Pos_Before=0;
2998 size_t Loop=0;
2999 do
3000 {
3001 size_t Data_Pos=Data.find(__T(" - "), Data_Pos_Before);
3002 if (Data_Pos==std::string::npos)
3003 Data_Pos=Data.size();
3004 if (Data.find(__T("options: "), Data_Pos_Before)==Data_Pos_Before)
3005 {
3006 Element_Begin1("options");
3007 size_t Options_Pos_Before=Data_Pos_Before;
3008 Encoded_Library_Settings.clear();
3009 do
3010 {
3011 size_t Options_Pos=Data.find(__T(" "), Options_Pos_Before);
3012 if (Options_Pos==std::string::npos)
3013 Options_Pos=Data.size();
3014 Ztring option;
3015 Get_Local (Options_Pos-Options_Pos_Before, option, "option");
3016 Options_Pos_Before=Options_Pos;
3017 do
3018 {
3019 Ztring Separator;
3020 Peek_Local(1, Separator);
3021 if (Separator==__T(" "))
3022 {
3023 Skip_Local(1, "separator");
3024 Options_Pos_Before+=1;
3025 }
3026 else
3027 break;
3028 }
3029 while (Options_Pos_Before!=Data.size());
3030
3031 //Filling
3032 if (option!=__T("options:"))
3033 {
3034 if (!Encoded_Library_Settings.empty())
3035 Encoded_Library_Settings+=__T(" / ");
3036 Encoded_Library_Settings+=option;
3037 if (option.find(__T("bitrate="))==0)
3038 BitRate_Nominal=option.substr(8)+__T("000"); //After "bitrate="
3039 }
3040 }
3041 while (Options_Pos_Before!=Data.size());
3042 Element_End0();
3043 }
3044 else
3045 {
3046 Ztring Value;
3047 Get_Local(Data_Pos-Data_Pos_Before, Value, "data");
3048
3049 //Saving
3050 if (Loop==0)
3051 {
3052 //Cleaning a little the value
3053 while (!Value.empty() && Value[0]<0x30)
3054 Value.erase(Value.begin());
3055 while (!Value.empty() && Value[Value.size()-1]<0x30)
3056 Value.erase(Value.end()-1);
3057 Encoded_Library=Value;
3058 }
3059 if (Loop==1 && Encoded_Library.find(__T("x264"))==0)
3060 {
3061 Encoded_Library+=__T(" - ");
3062 Encoded_Library+=Value;
3063 }
3064 }
3065 Data_Pos_Before=Data_Pos;
3066 if (Data_Pos_Before+3<=Data.size())
3067 {
3068 Skip_Local(3, "separator");
3069 Data_Pos_Before+=3;
3070 }
3071
3072 Loop++;
3073 }
3074 while (Data_Pos_Before!=Data.size());
3075
3076 //Encoded_Library
3077 if (Encoded_Library.find(__T("eavc "))==0)
3078 {
3079 Encoded_Library_Name=__T("eavc");
3080 Encoded_Library_Version=Encoded_Library.SubString(__T("eavc "), __T(""));
3081 }
3082 else if (Encoded_Library.find(__T("x264 - "))==0)
3083 {
3084 Encoded_Library_Name=__T("x264");
3085 Encoded_Library_Version=Encoded_Library.SubString(__T("x264 - "), __T(""));
3086 }
3087 else if (Encoded_Library.find(__T("SUPER(C) by eRightSoft "))==0)
3088 {
3089 Encoded_Library_Name=__T("SUPER(C) by eRightSoft");
3090 Encoded_Library_Date=Ztring(__T("UTC "))+Encoded_Library.SubString(__T("2000-"), __T(" "));
3091 }
3092 else
3093 Encoded_Library_Name=Encoded_Library;
3094}

3150void File_Avc::seq_parameter_set()

3156 seq_parameter_set_struct* Data_Item_New=seq_parameter_set_data(seq_parameter_set_id);
3157 if (!Data_Item_New)
3158 return;
3159 Mark_1( );
3160 size_t BS_bits=Data_BS_Remain()%8;
3161 while (BS_bits)
3162 {
3163 Mark_0( );
3164 BS_bits--;
3165 }
3166 BS_End();
3167
3168 //Hack for 00003.m2ts: There is a trailing 0x89, why?
3169 if (Element_Offset+1==Element_Size)
3170 {
3171 int8u ToTest;
3172 Peek_B1(ToTest);
3173 if (ToTest==0x98)
3174 Skip_B1( "Unknown");
3175
3176 }
3177
3178 //Hack for : There is a trailing data, why?
3179 if (Element_Offset+4==Element_Size)
3180 {
3181 int32u ToTest;
3182 Peek_B4(ToTest);
3183 if (ToTest==0xE30633C0)
3184 Skip_B4( "Unknown");
3185 }
3186
3187 //NULL bytes
3188 while (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
3189 {
3190 int8u Null;
3191 Get_B1 (Null, "NULL byte");
3192 if (Null)
3193 Trusted_IsNot("Should be NULL byte");
3194 }
3195
3196 FILLING_BEGIN_PRECISE();
3197 //NextCode
3198 NextCode_Clear();
3199 NextCode_Add(0x08);
3200
3201 //Add
3202 seq_parameter_set_data_Add(seq_parameter_sets, seq_parameter_set_id, Data_Item_New);
3203
3204 //Autorisation of other streams
3205 Streams[0x08].Searching_Payload=true; //pic_parameter_set
3206 if (Streams[0x07].ShouldDuplicate)
3207 Streams[0x08].ShouldDuplicate=true; //pic_parameter_set
3208 Streams[0x0A].Searching_Payload=true; //end_of_seq
3209 if (Streams[0x07].ShouldDuplicate)
3210 Streams[0x0A].ShouldDuplicate=true; //end_of_seq
3211 Streams[0x0B].Searching_Payload=true; //end_of_stream
3212 if (Streams[0x07].ShouldDuplicate)
3213 Streams[0x0B].ShouldDuplicate=true; //end_of_stream
3214 FILLING_END();
3215}
3216
3217void File_Avc::seq_parameter_set_data_Add(std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*> &Data, const int32u Data_id, seq_parameter_set_struct* Data_Item_New)
3218{
3219 //Creating Data
3220 if (Data_id>=Data.size())
3221 Data.resize(Data_id+1);
3222 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator Data_Item=Data.begin()+Data_id;
3223 delete *Data_Item; *Data_Item=Data_Item_New;
3224
3225 //Computing values (for speed)
3226 size_t MaxNumber;
3227 switch (Data_Item_New->pic_order_cnt_type)
3228 {
3229 case 0 :
3230 MaxNumber=Data_Item_New->MaxPicOrderCntLsb;
3231 break;
3232 case 1 :
3233 case 2 :
3234 MaxNumber=Data_Item_New->MaxFrameNum*2;
3235 break;
3236 default:
3237 MaxNumber = 0;
3238 }
3239
3240 if (MaxNumber>TemporalReferences_Reserved)
3241 {
3242 TemporalReferences.resize(4*MaxNumber);
3243 TemporalReferences_Reserved=MaxNumber;
3244 }
3245}
3246
3247//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3248// Packet "08"
3249void File_Avc::pic_parameter_set()
3250{
3251 Element_Name("pic_parameter_set");
3252
3253 //Parsing
3254 int32u pic_parameter_set_id, seq_parameter_set_id, num_slice_groups_minus1, num_ref_idx_l0_default_active_minus1, num_ref_idx_l1_default_active_minus1, slice_group_map_type=0;
3255 int8u weighted_bipred_idc=0;
3256 bool entropy_coding_mode_flag,bottom_field_pic_order_in_frame_present_flag, redundant_pic_cnt_present_flag, weighted_pred_flag, deblocking_filter_control_present_flag;
3257 BS_Begin();
3258 Get_UE (pic_parameter_set_id, "pic_parameter_set_id");
3259 Get_UE (seq_parameter_set_id, "seq_parameter_set_id");
3260 std::vector<seq_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator seq_parameter_set_Item;
3261 if (seq_parameter_set_id>=seq_parameter_sets.size() || (*(seq_parameter_set_Item=seq_parameter_sets.begin()+seq_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
3262 {
3263 if (seq_parameter_set_id>=subset_seq_parameter_sets.size() || (*(seq_parameter_set_Item=subset_seq_parameter_sets.begin()+seq_parameter_set_id))==NULL)
3264 {
3265 //Not yet present
3266 Skip_BS(Data_BS_Remain(), "Data (seq_parameter_set is missing)");
3267 return;
3268 }
3269 }
3270 Get_SB (entropy_coding_mode_flag, "entropy_coding_mode_flag");
3271 Get_SB (bottom_field_pic_order_in_frame_present_flag, "bottom_field_pic_order_in_frame_present_flag");
3272 Get_UE (num_slice_groups_minus1, "num_slice_groups_minus1");
3273 if (num_slice_groups_minus1>7)
3274 {
3275 Trusted_IsNot("num_slice_groups_minus1 too high");
3276 num_slice_groups_minus1=0;
3277 }
3278 if (num_slice_groups_minus1>0)
3279 {
3280 Get_UE (slice_group_map_type, "slice_group_map_type");
3281 if (slice_group_map_type==0)
3282 {
3283 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<=num_slice_groups_minus1; Pos++)
3284 Skip_UE( "run_length_minus1");
3285 }
3286 else if (slice_group_map_type==2)
3287 {
3288 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<num_slice_groups_minus1; Pos++)
3289 {
3290 Skip_UE( "top_left");
3291 Skip_UE( "bottom_right");
3292 }
3293 }
3294 else if (slice_group_map_type==3
3295 || slice_group_map_type==4
3296 || slice_group_map_type==5)
3297 {
3298 Skip_SB( "slice_group_change_direction_flag");
3299 Skip_UE( "slice_group_change_rate_minus1");
3300 }
3301 else if (slice_group_map_type==6)
3302 {
3303 int32u pic_size_in_map_units_minus1;
3304 Get_UE (pic_size_in_map_units_minus1, "pic_size_in_map_units_minus1");
3305 if(pic_size_in_map_units_minus1>((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_width_in_mbs_minus1+1)*((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->pic_height_in_map_units_minus1+1))
3306 {
3307 Trusted_IsNot("pic_size_in_map_units_minus1 too high");
3308 return;
3309 }
3310 #if defined (__mips__) || defined (__mipsel__)
3311 int32u slice_group_id_Size=(int32u)(std::ceil(std::log((double)(num_slice_groups_minus1+1))/std::log((double)10))); //std::log is natural logarithm
3312 #else
3313 int32u slice_group_id_Size=(int32u)(std::ceil(std::log((float32)(num_slice_groups_minus1+1))/std::log((float32)10))); //std::log is natural logarithm
3314 #endif
3315 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<=pic_size_in_map_units_minus1; Pos++)
3316 Skip_BS(slice_group_id_Size, "slice_group_id");
3317 }
3318 }
3319 Get_UE (num_ref_idx_l0_default_active_minus1, "num_ref_idx_l0_default_active_minus1");
3320 Get_UE (num_ref_idx_l1_default_active_minus1, "num_ref_idx_l1_default_active_minus1");
3321 Get_SB (weighted_pred_flag, "weighted_pred_flag");
3322 Get_S1 (2, weighted_bipred_idc, "weighted_bipred_idc");
3323 Skip_SE( "pic_init_qp_minus26");
3324 Skip_SE( "pic_init_qs_minus26");
3325 Skip_SE( "chroma_qp_index_offset");
3326 Get_SB (deblocking_filter_control_present_flag, "deblocking_filter_control_present_flag");
3327 Skip_SB( "constrained_intra_pred_flag");
3328 Get_SB (redundant_pic_cnt_present_flag, "redundant_pic_cnt_present_flag");
3329 bool more_rbsp_data=false;
3330 if (Element_Size)
3331 {
3332 int64u Offset=Element_Size-1;
3333 while (Offset && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Offset]==0x00) //Searching if there are NULL bytes at the end of the data
3334 Offset--;
3335 size_t Bit_Pos=7;
3336 while (Bit_Pos && !(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+(size_t)Offset]&(1<<(7-Bit_Pos))))
3337 Bit_Pos--;
3338 if (Data_BS_Remain()>1+(7-Bit_Pos)+(Element_Size-Offset-1)*8)
3339 more_rbsp_data=true;
3340 }
3341 if (more_rbsp_data)
3342 {
3343 bool transform_8x8_mode_flag;
3344 Get_SB (transform_8x8_mode_flag, "transform_8x8_mode_flag");
3345 TEST_SB_SKIP( "pic_scaling_matrix_present_flag");
3346 for (int8u Pos=0; Pos<6+(transform_8x8_mode_flag?((*seq_parameter_set_Item)->chroma_format_idc!=3?2:6):0); Pos++ )
3347 {
3348 TEST_SB_SKIP( "pic_scaling_list_present_flag");
3349 scaling_list(Pos<6?16:64);
3350 TEST_SB_END();
3351 }
3352 TEST_SB_END();
3353 Skip_SE( "second_chroma_qp_index_offset");
3354 }
3355 Mark_1( );
3356 BS_End();
3357
3358 while (Element_Offset<Element_Size) //Not always removed from the stream, ie in MPEG-4
3359 {
3360 int8u Padding;
3361 Peek_B1(Padding);
3362 if (!Padding)
3363 Skip_B1( "Padding");
3364 else
3365 break;
3366 }
3367
3368 FILLING_BEGIN_PRECISE();
3369 //Integrity
3370 if (pic_parameter_set_id>=256)
3371 {
3372 Trusted_IsNot("pic_parameter_set_id not valid");
3373 return; //Problem, not valid
3374 }
3375 if (seq_parameter_set_id>=32)
3376 {
3377 Trusted_IsNot("seq_parameter_set_id not valid");
3378 return; //Problem, not valid
3379 }
3380
3381 //NextCode
3382 NextCode_Clear();
3383 NextCode_Add(0x05);
3384 NextCode_Add(0x06);
3385 if (!subset_seq_parameter_sets.empty())
3386 NextCode_Add(0x14); //slice_layer_extension
3387
3388 //Filling
3389 if (pic_parameter_set_id>=pic_parameter_sets.size())
3390 pic_parameter_sets.resize(pic_parameter_set_id+1);
3391 std::vector<pic_parameter_set_struct*>::iterator pic_parameter_sets_Item=pic_parameter_sets.begin()+pic_parameter_set_id;
3392 delete *pic_parameter_sets_Item; *pic_parameter_sets_Item = new pic_parameter_set_struct(
3393 (int8u)seq_parameter_set_id,
3394 (int8u)num_ref_idx_l0_default_active_minus1,
3395 (int8u)num_ref_idx_l1_default_active_minus1,
3396 weighted_bipred_idc,
3397 num_slice_groups_minus1,
3398 slice_group_map_type,
3399 entropy_coding_mode_flag,
3400 bottom_field_pic_order_in_frame_present_flag,
3401 weighted_pred_flag,
3402 redundant_pic_cnt_present_flag,
3403 deblocking_filter_control_present_flag
3404 );
3405
3406 //Autorisation of other streams
3407 if (!seq_parameter_sets.empty())
3408 {
3409 for (int8u Pos=0x01; Pos<=0x06; Pos++)
3410 {
3411 Streams[Pos].Searching_Payload=true; //Coded slice...
3412 if (Streams[0x08].ShouldDuplicate)
3413 Streams[Pos].ShouldDuplicate=true;
3414 }
3415 }
3416 if (!subset_seq_parameter_sets.empty())
3417 {
3418 Streams[0x14].Searching_Payload=true; //slice_layer_extension
3419 if (Streams[0x08].ShouldDuplicate)
3420 Streams[0x14].ShouldDuplicate=true; //slice_layer_extension
3421 }
3422
3423 //Setting as OK
3424 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
3425 Accept("AVC");
3426 FILLING_END();
3427}

3431void File_Avc::access_unit_delimiter()
3432{

3434

3442//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3443// Packet "09"
3444void File_Avc::filler_data()
3445{
3446 Element_Name("filler_data");
3447
3448 while (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
3449 {
3450 int8u FF;
3451 Peek_B1(FF);
3452 if (FF!=0xFF)
3453 break;
3454 Element_Offset++;
3455 }
3456 BS_Begin();
3457 Mark_1( );
3458 BS_End();
3459}

3500 /* The rest is not yet implemented

3512 }

3515 */

3531 if (Streams[0x0F].ShouldDuplicate)
3532 Streams[0x0A].ShouldDuplicate=true; //end_of_seq
3533 Streams[0x0B].Searching_Payload=true; //end_of_stream
3534 if (Streams[0x0F].ShouldDuplicate)
3535 Streams[0x0B].ShouldDuplicate=true; //end_of_stream

3560// SubElements
3561//***************************************************************************
3562
3563//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3564File_Avc::seq_parameter_set_struct* File_Avc::seq_parameter_set_data(int32u &Data_id)
3565{
3566 //Parsing
3567 seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct* vui_parameters_Item=NULL;
3568 int32u chroma_format_idc=1, bit_depth_luma_minus8=0, bit_depth_chroma_minus8=0, log2_max_frame_num_minus4, pic_order_cnt_type, log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4=(int32u)-1, max_num_ref_frames, pic_width_in_mbs_minus1, pic_height_in_map_units_minus1, frame_crop_left_offset=0, frame_crop_right_offset=0, frame_crop_top_offset=0, frame_crop_bottom_offset=0;
3569 int8u profile_idc, level_idc;
3570 bool constraint_set3_flag, separate_colour_plane_flag=false, delta_pic_order_always_zero_flag=false, frame_mbs_only_flag, mb_adaptive_frame_field_flag=false;
3571 Get_B1 (profile_idc, "profile_idc");
3572 BS_Begin();
3573 Element_Begin1("constraints");
3574 Skip_SB( "constraint_set0_flag");
3575 Skip_SB( "constraint_set1_flag");
3576 Skip_SB( "constraint_set2_flag");
3577 Get_SB (constraint_set3_flag, "constraint_set3_flag");
3578 Skip_SB( "constraint_set4_flag");
3579 Skip_SB( "constraint_set5_flag");
3580 Skip_BS(2, "reserved_zero_2bits");
3581 Element_End0();
3582 Get_S1 ( 8, level_idc, "level_idc");
3583 Get_UE ( Data_id, "seq_parameter_set_id");
3584 switch (profile_idc)
3585 {
3586 case 100 :
3587 case 110 :
3588 case 122 :
3589 case 244 :
3590 case 44 :
3591 case 83 :
3592 case 86 :
3593 case 118 :
3594 case 128 : //High profiles
3595 case 138 :
3596 Element_Begin1("high profile specific");
3597 Get_UE (chroma_format_idc, "chroma_format_idc"); Param_Info1C((chroma_format_idc<3), Avc_Colorimetry_format_idc[chroma_format_idc]);
3598 if (chroma_format_idc==3)
3599 Get_SB (separate_colour_plane_flag, "separate_colour_plane_flag");
3600 Get_UE (bit_depth_luma_minus8, "bit_depth_luma_minus8");
3601 Get_UE (bit_depth_chroma_minus8, "bit_depth_chroma_minus8");
3602 Skip_SB( "qpprime_y_zero_transform_bypass_flag");
3603 TEST_SB_SKIP( "seq_scaling_matrix_present_flag");
3604 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<(int32u)((chroma_format_idc!=3) ? 8 : 12); Pos++)
3605 {
3606 TEST_SB_SKIP( "seq_scaling_list_present_flag");
3607 scaling_list(Pos<6?16:64);
3608 TEST_SB_END();
3609 }
3610 TEST_SB_END();
3611 Element_End0();
3612 break;
3613 default : ;
3614 }
3615 Get_UE (log2_max_frame_num_minus4, "log2_max_frame_num_minus4");
3616 Get_UE (pic_order_cnt_type, "pic_order_cnt_type");
3617 if (pic_order_cnt_type==0)
3618 Get_UE (log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4, "log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4");
3619 else if (pic_order_cnt_type==1)
3620 {
3621 int32u num_ref_frames_in_pic_order_cnt_cycle;
3622 Get_SB (delta_pic_order_always_zero_flag, "delta_pic_order_always_zero_flag");
3623 Skip_SE( "offset_for_non_ref_pic");
3624 Skip_SE( "offset_for_top_to_bottom_field");
3625 Get_UE (num_ref_frames_in_pic_order_cnt_cycle, "num_ref_frames_in_pic_order_cnt_cycle");
3626 if (num_ref_frames_in_pic_order_cnt_cycle>=256)
3627 {
3628 Trusted_IsNot("num_ref_frames_in_pic_order_cnt_cycle too high");
3629 return NULL;
3630 }
3631 for(int32u Pos=0; Pos<num_ref_frames_in_pic_order_cnt_cycle; Pos++)
3632 Skip_SE( "offset_for_ref_frame");
3633 }
3634 else if (pic_order_cnt_type > 2)
3635 {
3636 Trusted_IsNot("pic_order_cnt_type not supported");
3637 return NULL;
3638 }
3639 Get_UE (max_num_ref_frames, "max_num_ref_frames");
3640 Skip_SB( "gaps_in_frame_num_value_allowed_flag");
3641 Get_UE (pic_width_in_mbs_minus1, "pic_width_in_mbs_minus1");
3642 Get_UE (pic_height_in_map_units_minus1, "pic_height_in_map_units_minus1");
3643 Get_SB (frame_mbs_only_flag, "frame_mbs_only_flag");
3644 if (!frame_mbs_only_flag)
3645 Get_SB (mb_adaptive_frame_field_flag, "mb_adaptive_frame_field_flag");
3646 Skip_SB( "direct_8x8_inference_flag");
3647 TEST_SB_SKIP( "frame_cropping_flag");
3648 Get_UE (frame_crop_left_offset, "frame_crop_left_offset");
3649 Get_UE (frame_crop_right_offset, "frame_crop_right_offset");
3650 Get_UE (frame_crop_top_offset, "frame_crop_top_offset");
3651 Get_UE (frame_crop_bottom_offset, "frame_crop_bottom_offset");
3652 TEST_SB_END();
3653 TEST_SB_SKIP( "vui_parameters_present_flag");
3654 vui_parameters(vui_parameters_Item);
3655 TEST_SB_END();
3656
3657 FILLING_BEGIN();
3658 //Integrity
3659 if (Data_id>=32)
3660 {
3661 Trusted_IsNot("seq_parameter_set_id not valid");
3662 delete (seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct*)vui_parameters_Item;
3663 return NULL; //Problem, not valid
3664 }
3665 if (pic_order_cnt_type==0 && log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4>12)
3666 {
3667 Trusted_IsNot("log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4 not valid");
3668 delete (seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct*)vui_parameters_Item;
3669 return NULL; //Problem, not valid
3670 }
3671 if (log2_max_frame_num_minus4>12)
3672 {
3673 Trusted_IsNot("log2_max_frame_num_minus4 not valid");
3674 delete (seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct*)vui_parameters_Item;
3675 return NULL; //Problem, not valid
3676 }
3677
3678 //Creating Data
3679 return new seq_parameter_set_struct(
3680 vui_parameters_Item,
3681 pic_width_in_mbs_minus1,
3682 pic_height_in_map_units_minus1,
3683 frame_crop_left_offset,
3684 frame_crop_right_offset,
3685 frame_crop_top_offset,
3686 frame_crop_bottom_offset,
3687 (int8u)chroma_format_idc,
3688 profile_idc,
3689 level_idc,
3690 (int8u)bit_depth_luma_minus8,
3691 (int8u)bit_depth_chroma_minus8,
3692 (int8u)log2_max_frame_num_minus4,
3693 (int8u)pic_order_cnt_type,
3694 (int8u)log2_max_pic_order_cnt_lsb_minus4,
3695 (int8u)max_num_ref_frames,
3696 constraint_set3_flag,
3697 separate_colour_plane_flag,
3698 delta_pic_order_always_zero_flag,
3699 frame_mbs_only_flag,
3700 mb_adaptive_frame_field_flag
3701 );
3702 FILLING_ELSE();
3703 delete vui_parameters_Item; //vui_parameters_Item=NULL;
3704 return NULL;
3705 FILLING_END();
3706}
3707
3708//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3709void File_Avc::scaling_list(int32u ScalingList_Size)
3710{
3711 //From http://mpeg4ip.cvs.sourceforge.net/mpeg4ip/mpeg4ip/util/h264/main.cpp?revision=1.17&view=markup
3712 int32u lastScale=8, nextScale=8;
3713 for (int32u Pos=0; Pos<ScalingList_Size; Pos++)
3714 {
3715 if (nextScale!=0)
3716 {
3717 int32s delta_scale;
3718 Get_SE (delta_scale, "scale_delta");
3719 nextScale=(lastScale+delta_scale+256)%256;
3720 }
3721 if (nextScale)
3722 lastScale=nextScale;
3723 }
3724}

3733 int16u sar_width=(int16u)-1, sar_height=(int16u)-1;
3734 int8u aspect_ratio_idc=0, video_format=5, video_full_range_flag = 0, colour_primaries=2, transfer_characteristics=2, matrix_coefficients=2;
3735 bool aspect_ratio_info_present_flag, video_signal_type_present_flag, colour_description_present_flag=false, timing_info_present_flag, fixed_frame_rate_flag=false, nal_hrd_parameters_present_flag, vcl_hrd_parameters_present_flag, pic_struct_present_flag;
3736 TEST_SB_GET (aspect_ratio_info_present_flag, "aspect_ratio_info_present_flag");
3737 Get_S1 (8, aspect_ratio_idc, "aspect_ratio_idc"); Param_Info1C((aspect_ratio_idc<Avc_PixelAspectRatio_Size), Avc_PixelAspectRatio[aspect_ratio_idc]);
3738 if (aspect_ratio_idc==0xFF)

3741 Get_S2 (16, sar_height, "sar_height");

3743 TEST_SB_END();
3744 TEST_SB_SKIP( "overscan_info_present_flag");
3745 Skip_SB( "overscan_appropriate_flag");
3746 TEST_SB_END();
3747 TEST_SB_GET (video_signal_type_present_flag, "video_signal_type_present_flag");
3748 Get_S1 (3, video_format, "video_format"); Param_Info1(Avc_video_format[video_format]);

3753 Get_S1 (8, matrix_coefficients, "matrix_coefficients"); Param_Info1(Mpegv_matrix_coefficients(matrix_coefficients));
3754 TEST_SB_END();
3755 TEST_SB_END();
3756 TEST_SB_SKIP( "chroma_loc_info_present_flag");
3757 Skip_UE( "chroma_sample_loc_type_top_field");
3758 Skip_UE( "chroma_sample_loc_type_bottom_field");
3759 TEST_SB_END();
3760 TEST_SB_GET (timing_info_present_flag, "timing_info_present_flag");
3761 Get_S4 (32, num_units_in_tick, "num_units_in_tick");
3762 Get_S4 (32, time_scale, "time_scale");
3763 Get_SB ( fixed_frame_rate_flag, "fixed_frame_rate_flag");
3764 TEST_SB_END();

3766 hrd_parameters(NAL);

3786 );

3818//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3819void File_Avc::hrd_parameters(seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct::xxl* &hrd_parameters_Item_)
3820{
3821 //Parsing
3822 int32u cpb_cnt_minus1;
3823 int8u bit_rate_scale, cpb_size_scale, initial_cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1, cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1, dpb_output_delay_length_minus1, time_offset_length;
3824 Get_UE ( cpb_cnt_minus1, "cpb_cnt_minus1");
3825 Get_S1 (4, bit_rate_scale, "bit_rate_scale");
3826 Get_S1 (4, cpb_size_scale, "cpb_size_scale");
3827 if (cpb_cnt_minus1>31)
3828 {
3829 Trusted_IsNot("cpb_cnt_minus1 too high");
3830 cpb_cnt_minus1=0;
3831 }
3832 vector<seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct::xxl::xxl_data> SchedSel;
3833 SchedSel.reserve(cpb_cnt_minus1+1);
3834 for (int8u SchedSelIdx = 0; SchedSelIdx <= cpb_cnt_minus1; ++SchedSelIdx)
3835 {
3836 Element_Begin1("ShedSel");
3837 int64u bit_rate_value, cpb_size_value;
3838 int32u bit_rate_value_minus1, cpb_size_value_minus1;
3839 bool cbr_flag;
3840 Get_UE (bit_rate_value_minus1, "bit_rate_value_minus1");
3841 bit_rate_value=(int64u)((bit_rate_value_minus1+1)*pow(2.0, 6+bit_rate_scale)); Param_Info2(bit_rate_value, " bps");
3842 Get_UE (cpb_size_value_minus1, "cpb_size_value_minus1");
3843 cpb_size_value=(int64u)((cpb_size_value_minus1+1)*pow(2.0, 4+cpb_size_scale)); Param_Info2(cpb_size_value, " bits");
3844 Get_SB (cbr_flag, "cbr_flag");
3845 Element_End0();
3846
3847 FILLING_BEGIN();
3848 SchedSel.push_back(seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct::xxl::xxl_data(
3849 bit_rate_value,
3850 cpb_size_value,
3851 cbr_flag
3852 ));
3853 FILLING_END();
3854 }
3855 Get_S1 (5, initial_cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1, "initial_cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1");
3856 Get_S1 (5, cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1, "cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1");
3857 Get_S1 (5, dpb_output_delay_length_minus1, "dpb_output_delay_length_minus1");
3858 Get_S1 (5, time_offset_length, "time_offset_length");
3859
3860 //Validity test
3861 if (!Element_IsOK() || (SchedSel.size() == 1 && SchedSel[0].bit_rate_value == 64))
3862 {
3863 return; //We do not trust this kind of data
3864 }
3865
3866 //Filling
3867 hrd_parameters_Item_=new seq_parameter_set_struct::vui_parameters_struct::xxl(
3868 SchedSel,
3869 initial_cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1,
3870 cpb_removal_delay_length_minus1,
3871 dpb_output_delay_length_minus1,
3872 time_offset_length
3873 );
3874}

3954
3955//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
3956void File_Avc::SPS_PPS()
3957{
3958 //Parsing
3959 int8u Profile, Level, seq_parameter_set_count, pic_parameter_set_count;
3960 if (SizedBlocks)
3961 Skip_B1( "Version");
3962 Get_B1 (Profile, "Profile");
3963 Skip_B1( "Compatible profile");
3964 Get_B1 (Level, "Level");
3965 BS_Begin();
3966 Skip_S1(6, "Reserved");
3967 Get_S1 (2, SizeOfNALU_Minus1, "Size of NALU length minus 1");
3968 Skip_S1(3, "Reserved");
3969 Get_S1 (5, seq_parameter_set_count, "seq_parameter_set count");
3970 BS_End();
3971 for (int8u Pos=0; Pos<seq_parameter_set_count; Pos++)
3972 {
3973 Element_Begin1("seq_parameter_set");
3974 int16u Size;
3975 Get_B2 (Size, "Size");
3976 BS_Begin();
3977 Mark_0 ();
3978 Skip_S1( 2, "nal_ref_idc");
3979 Skip_S1( 5, "nal_unit_type");
3980 BS_End();
3981 if (Element_Offset+Size-1>Element_Size)
3982 {
3983 Trusted_IsNot("Size is wrong");
3984 break; //There is an error
3985 }
3986 int64u Element_Offset_Save=Element_Offset;
3987 int64u Element_Size_Save=Element_Size;
3988 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset_Save;
3989 Element_Offset=0;
3990 Element_Size=Size-(Size?1:0);
3991 Element_Code=0x07; //seq_parameter_set
3992 Data_Parse();
3993 Buffer_Offset-=(size_t)Element_Offset_Save;
3994 Element_Offset=Element_Offset_Save+Size-1;
3995 Element_Size=Element_Size_Save;
3996 Element_End0();
3997 }
3998 Get_B1 (pic_parameter_set_count, "pic_parameter_set count");
3999 for (int8u Pos=0; Pos<pic_parameter_set_count; Pos++)
4000 {
4001 Element_Begin1("pic_parameter_set");
4002 int16u Size;
4003 Get_B2 (Size, "Size");
4004 BS_Begin();
4005 Mark_0 ();
4006 Skip_S1( 2, "nal_ref_idc");
4007 Skip_S1( 5, "nal_unit_type");
4008 BS_End();
4009 int64u Element_Offset_Save=Element_Offset;
4010 int64u Element_Size_Save=Element_Size;
4011 Buffer_Offset+=(size_t)Element_Offset_Save;
4012 Element_Offset=0;
4013 Element_Size=Size-1;
4014 if (Element_Size>Element_Size_Save-Element_Offset_Save)
4015 break; //There is an error
4016 Element_Code=0x08; //pic_parameter_set
4017 Data_Parse();
4018 Buffer_Offset-=(size_t)Element_Offset_Save;
4019 Element_Offset=Element_Offset_Save+Size-1;
4020 Element_Size=Element_Size_Save;
4021 Element_End0();
4022 }
4023 if (Element_Offset<Element_Size)
4024 Skip_XX(Element_Size-Element_Offset, "Padding?");
4025
4026 //Filling
4027 FILLING_BEGIN_PRECISE();
4028 //Detection of some bugs in the file
4029 if (!seq_parameter_sets.empty() && seq_parameter_sets[0] && (Profile!=seq_parameter_sets[0]->profile_idc || Level!=seq_parameter_sets[0]->level_idc))
4030 MuxingMode=Ztring("Container profile=")+Ztring().From_Local(Avc_profile_idc(Profile))+__T("@")+Ztring().From_Number(((float)Level)/10, 1);
4031
4032 MustParse_SPS_PPS=false;
4033 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
4034 Accept("AVC");
4035 FILLING_END();
4036}

4041
4042//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4043std::string File_Avc::GOP_Detect (std::string PictureTypes)
4044{
4045 //Finding a string without blanks
4046 size_t PictureTypes_Limit=PictureTypes.find(' ');
4047 if (PictureTypes_Limit!=string::npos)
4048 {
4049 if (PictureTypes_Limit>PictureTypes.size()/2)
4050 PictureTypes.resize(PictureTypes_Limit);
4051 else
4052 {
4053 //Trim
4054 size_t TrimPos;
4055 TrimPos=PictureTypes.find_first_not_of(' ');
4056 if (TrimPos!=string::npos)
4057 PictureTypes.erase(0, TrimPos);
4058 TrimPos=PictureTypes.find_last_not_of(' ');
4059 if (TrimPos!=string::npos)
4060 PictureTypes.erase(TrimPos+1);
4061
4062 //Finding the longest string
4063 ZtringList List; List.Separator_Set(0, __T(" "));
4064 List.Write(Ztring().From_Local(PictureTypes));
4065 size_t MaxLength=0;
4066 size_t MaxLength_Pos=0;
4067 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<List.size(); Pos++)
4068 if (List[Pos].size()>MaxLength)
4069 {
4070 MaxLength=List[Pos].size();
4071 MaxLength_Pos=Pos;
4072 }
4073 PictureTypes=List[MaxLength_Pos].To_Local();
4074
4075 }
4076 }
4077
4078 //Creating all GOP values
4079 std::vector<Ztring> GOPs;
4080 size_t GOP_Frame_Count=0;
4081 size_t GOP_BFrames_Max=0;
4082 size_t I_Pos1=PictureTypes.find('I');
4083 while (I_Pos1!=std::string::npos)
4084 {
4085 size_t I_Pos2=PictureTypes.find('I', I_Pos1+1);
4086 if (I_Pos2!=std::string::npos)
4087 {
4088 std::vector<size_t> P_Positions;
4089 size_t P_Position=I_Pos1;
4090 do
4091 {
4092 P_Position=PictureTypes.find('P', P_Position+1);
4093 if (P_Position<I_Pos2)
4094 P_Positions.push_back(P_Position);
4095 }
4096 while (P_Position<I_Pos2);
4097 if (P_Positions.size()>1 && P_Positions[0]>I_Pos1+1 && P_Positions[P_Positions.size()-1]==I_Pos2-1)
4098 P_Positions.resize(P_Positions.size()-1); //Removing last P-Frame for next test, this is often a terminating P-Frame replacing a B-Frame
4099 Ztring GOP;
4100 bool IsOK=true;
4101 if (!P_Positions.empty())
4102 {
4103 size_t Delta=P_Positions[0]-I_Pos1;
4104 for (size_t Pos=1; Pos<P_Positions.size(); Pos++)
4105 if (P_Positions[Pos]-P_Positions[Pos-1]!=Delta)
4106 {
4107 IsOK=false;
4108 break;
4109 }
4110 if (IsOK)
4111 {
4112 GOP+=__T("M=")+Ztring::ToZtring(P_Positions[0]-I_Pos1)+__T(", ");
4113 if (P_Positions[0]-I_Pos1>GOP_BFrames_Max)
4114 GOP_BFrames_Max=P_Positions[0]-I_Pos1;
4115 }
4116 }
4117 if (IsOK)
4118 {
4119 GOP+=__T("N=")+Ztring::ToZtring(I_Pos2-I_Pos1);
4120 GOPs.push_back(GOP);
4121 }
4122 else
4123 GOPs.push_back(Ztring()); //There is a problem, blank
4124 GOP_Frame_Count+=I_Pos2-I_Pos1;
4125 }
4126 I_Pos1=I_Pos2;
4127 }
4128
4129 //Some clean up
4130 if (GOP_Frame_Count+GOP_BFrames_Max>Frame_Count && !GOPs.empty())
4131 GOPs.resize(GOPs.size()-1); //Removing the last one, there may have uncomplete B-frame filling
4132 if (GOPs.size()>4)
4133 GOPs.erase(GOPs.begin()); //Removing the first one, it is sometime different and we have enough to deal with
4134
4135 //Filling
4136 if (GOPs.size()>=4)
4137 {
4138 bool IsOK=true;
4139 for (size_t Pos=1; Pos<GOPs.size(); Pos++)
4140 if (GOPs[Pos]!=GOPs[0])
4141 {
4142 IsOK=false;
4143 break;
4144 }
4145 if (IsOK)
4146 return GOPs[0].To_Local();
4147 }
4148
4149 return string();
4150}
4151
4152//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
4153std::string File_Avc::ScanOrder_Detect (std::string ScanOrders)
4154{
4155 //Finding a string without blanks
4156 size_t ScanOrders_Limit=ScanOrders.find(' ');
4157 if (ScanOrders_Limit!=string::npos)
4158 {
4159 if (ScanOrders_Limit>ScanOrders.size()/2)
4160 ScanOrders.resize(ScanOrders_Limit);
4161 else
4162 {
4163 //Trim
4164 size_t TrimPos;
4165 TrimPos=ScanOrders.find_first_not_of(' ');
4166 if (TrimPos!=string::npos)
4167 ScanOrders.erase(0, TrimPos);
4168 TrimPos=ScanOrders.find_last_not_of(' ');
4169 if (TrimPos!=string::npos)
4170 ScanOrders.erase(TrimPos+1);
4171
4172 //Finding the longest string
4173 ZtringList List; List.Separator_Set(0, __T(" "));
4174 List.Write(Ztring().From_Local(ScanOrders));
4175 size_t MaxLength=0;
4176 size_t MaxLength_Pos=0;
4177 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<List.size(); Pos++)
4178 if (List[Pos].size()>MaxLength)
4179 {
4180 MaxLength=List[Pos].size();
4181 MaxLength_Pos=Pos;
4182 }
4183 ScanOrders=List[MaxLength_Pos].To_Local();
4184
4185 }
4186 }
4187
4188 //Filling
4189 if (ScanOrders.find("TBTBTBTB")==0)
4190 return ("TFF");
4191 if (ScanOrders.find("BTBTBTBT")==0)
4192 return ("BFF");
4193 return string();
4194}
